module.exports = [
  // === AWS (1-25) ===
  { id: 1, title: 'AWS คืออะไร', description: 'แสดงข้อความ "AWS = Amazon Web Services" และ "Cloud Computing Platform"', difficulty: 1, category: 'aws', hint: 'ใช้ echo 2 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 AWS (Amazon Web Services) คือแพลตฟอร์ม Cloud Computing ของ Amazon\n\nให้บริการ:\n  - Compute (EC2, Lambda)\n  - Storage (S3, EBS)\n  - Database (RDS, DynamoDB)\n  - Networking (VPC, Route53)\n  - และอีกกว่า 200+ services\n\nข้อดี:\n  - จ่ายตามการใช้งาน (Pay-as-you-go)\n  - มี Data Center ทั่วโลก (Regions & AZs)\n  - Scale ได้ตามต้องการ\n  - มี Free Tier สำหรับเริ่มต้น', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'AWS = Amazon Web Services\nCloud Computing Platform', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 2, title: 'AWS Regions & AZs', description: 'แสดง "Region: us-east-1", "AZ-1: us-east-1a", "AZ-2: us-east-1b", "AZ-3: us-east-1c"', difficulty: 1, category: 'aws', hint: 'echo 4 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 AWS แบ่งโครงสร้างเป็น Region และ Availability Zone (AZ)\n\nRegion = พื้นที่ทางภูมิศาสตร์ (เช่น us-east-1 = Virginia)\nAZ = Data Center ภายใน Region (เช่น us-east-1a, us-east-1b)\n\nแต่ละ Region มี 2-6 AZs\nAZs เชื่อมกันด้วย network ความเร็วสูง\n\nเลือก Region ตาม:\n  - ใกล้ผู้ใช้ (latency ต่ำ)\n  - ราคา (แต่ละ Region ราคาต่างกัน)\n  - Compliance (กฎหมายข้อมูล)\n  - Services ที่ต้องการ (บาง service ไม่มีทุก Region)', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Region: us-east-1\nAZ-1: us-east-1a\nAZ-2: us-east-1b\nAZ-3: us-east-1c', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 3, title: 'AWS IAM', description: 'แสดง "Service: IAM", "User: devops-admin", "Group: developers", "Role: EC2-S3-Access", "Policy: AmazonS3ReadOnly"', difficulty: 1, category: 'aws', hint: 'echo 5 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 IAM (Identity and Access Management) จัดการสิทธิ์การเข้าถึง AWS\n\nส่วนประกอบ:\n  User = บัญชีผู้ใช้ (คน หรือ application)\n  Group = กลุ่มของ Users (กำหนดสิทธิ์รวม)\n  Role = สิทธิ์สำหรับ AWS Services (เช่น EC2 เข้าถึง S3)\n  Policy = เอกสาร JSON กำหนดสิทธิ์\n\nBest Practices:\n  - ใช้ Root Account เฉพาะตั้งค่าครั้งแรก\n  - เปิด MFA ทุก account\n  - ใช้ Least Privilege (ให้สิทธิ์น้อยที่สุดที่จำเป็น)\n  - ใช้ Role แทน Access Key เมื่อทำได้', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Service: IAM\nUser: devops-admin\nGroup: developers\nRole: EC2-S3-Access\nPolicy: AmazonS3ReadOnly', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 4, title: 'AWS EC2', description: 'แสดง "Service: EC2", "Instance: i-0abc123", "Type: t3.micro", "State: running", "vCPU: 2, RAM: 1GB"', difficulty: 1, category: 'aws', hint: 'echo 5 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 EC2 (Elastic Compute Cloud) = Virtual Server บน AWS\n\nInstance Types:\n  t3.micro  = 2 vCPU, 1GB RAM (Free Tier)\n  t3.small  = 2 vCPU, 2GB RAM\n  m5.large  = 2 vCPU, 8GB RAM\n  c5.xlarge = 4 vCPU, 8GB RAM (compute optimized)\n\nPricing Models:\n  On-Demand = จ่ายรายชั่วโมง\n  Reserved = จอง 1-3 ปี (ลด 30-60%)\n  Spot = ประมูลราคา (ลดสูงสุด 90%)\n\nสิ่งที่ต้องเลือก: AMI (OS), Instance Type, VPC/Subnet, Security Group, Key Pair', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Service: EC2\nInstance: i-0abc123\nType: t3.micro\nState: running\nvCPU: 2, RAM: 1GB', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 5, title: 'AWS S3', description: 'แสดง "Service: S3", "Bucket: my-app-data", "Region: us-east-1", "Objects: 1,250", "Size: 5.2 GB"', difficulty: 1, category: 'aws', hint: 'echo 5 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 S3 (Simple Storage Service) = Object Storage ไม่จำกัดขนาด\n\nแนวคิด:\n  Bucket = ที่เก็บ (ชื่อต้อง unique ทั่วโลก)\n  Object = ไฟล์ + metadata (สูงสุด 5TB/object)\n  Key = path ของ object (เช่น images/photo.jpg)\n\nStorage Classes:\n  Standard = เข้าถึงบ่อย\n  Standard-IA = เข้าถึงไม่บ่อย (ถูกกว่า)\n  Glacier = archive ระยะยาว (ถูกมาก)\n\nใช้งาน: Static website hosting, Backup, Data lake, CDN origin', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Service: S3\nBucket: my-app-data\nRegion: us-east-1\nObjects: 1,250\nSize: 5.2 GB', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 6, title: 'AWS VPC', description: 'แสดง "Service: VPC", "CIDR: 10.0.0.0/16", "Public Subnet: 10.0.1.0/24", "Private Subnet: 10.0.2.0/24", "Internet Gateway: igw-abc123"', difficulty: 2, category: 'aws', hint: 'echo 5 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 VPC (Virtual Private Cloud) = เครือข่ายส่วนตัวบน AWS\n\nส่วนประกอบ:\n  VPC = เครือข่ายหลัก (เช่น 10.0.0.0/16 = 65,536 IPs)\n  Subnet = แบ่งย่อย VPC\n    - Public Subnet = เข้าถึงจาก internet ได้\n    - Private Subnet = เข้าถึงจาก internet ไม่ได้\n  Internet Gateway (IGW) = ประตูเชื่อม internet\n  NAT Gateway = ให้ private subnet ออก internet ได้\n  Route Table = กำหนดเส้นทาง traffic\n  Security Group = firewall ระดับ instance\n  NACL = firewall ระดับ subnet\n\nBest Practice: แยก public/private subnet, ใช้ multi-AZ', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Service: VPC\nCIDR: 10.0.0.0/16\nPublic Subnet: 10.0.1.0/24\nPrivate Subnet: 10.0.2.0/24\nInternet Gateway: igw-abc123', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 7, title: 'AWS Security Groups', description: 'แสดง "SG: web-server-sg", "Inbound: TCP 80 from 0.0.0.0/0", "Inbound: TCP 443 from 0.0.0.0/0", "Inbound: TCP 22 from 10.0.0.0/16", "Outbound: All traffic allowed"', difficulty: 2, category: 'aws', hint: 'echo 5 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Security Group = Virtual Firewall สำหรับ EC2\n\nคุณสมบัติ:\n  - Stateful (อนุญาตขาเข้า = ขาออกอัตโนมัติ)\n  - อนุญาตเท่านั้น (ไม่มี deny rules)\n  - ผูกกับ instance (ไม่ใช่ subnet)\n\nตัวอย่าง rules:\n  Web Server: เปิด port 80, 443 จากทุกที่\n  Database: เปิด port 3306 เฉพาะจาก app subnet\n  SSH: เปิด port 22 เฉพาะจาก VPN/office IP\n\nBest Practice: เปิดเฉพาะ port ที่จำเป็น, ไม่เปิด 0.0.0.0/0 สำหรับ SSH', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'SG: web-server-sg\nInbound: TCP 80 from 0.0.0.0/0\nInbound: TCP 443 from 0.0.0.0/0\nInbound: TCP 22 from 10.0.0.0/16\nOutbound: All traffic allowed', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 8, title: 'AWS Lambda', description: 'แสดง "Service: Lambda", "Function: process-order", "Runtime: python3.12", "Memory: 256MB", "Timeout: 30s", "Trigger: API Gateway"', difficulty: 2, category: 'aws', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Lambda = Serverless compute (รันโค้ดโดยไม่ต้องจัดการ server)\n\nทำงานอย่างไร:\n  1. เขียน function code\n  2. กำหนด trigger (เหตุการณ์ที่เรียก function)\n  3. Lambda รัน code เมื่อมี trigger\n  4. จ่ายเฉพาะเวลาที่ code ทำงาน\n\nTriggers ที่นิยม:\n  API Gateway = HTTP request\n  S3 = เมื่อมีไฟล์ใหม่\n  SQS = เมื่อมี message ใน queue\n  CloudWatch Events = ตั้งเวลา (cron)\n  DynamoDB Streams = เมื่อข้อมูลเปลี่ยน\n\nข้อจำกัด: timeout สูงสุด 15 นาที, memory สูงสุด 10GB', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Service: Lambda\nFunction: process-order\nRuntime: python3.12\nMemory: 256MB\nTimeout: 30s\nTrigger: API Gateway', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 9, title: 'AWS RDS', description: 'แสดง "Service: RDS", "Engine: PostgreSQL 15", "Instance: db.t3.medium", "Storage: 100GB gp3", "Multi-AZ: enabled", "Backup: 7 days"', difficulty: 2, category: 'aws', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 RDS (Relational Database Service) = Managed Database\n\nAWS จัดการให้:\n  - Provisioning & patching\n  - Automated backups\n  - Multi-AZ failover\n  - Read Replicas\n  - Encryption\n\nEngines ที่รองรับ:\n  MySQL, PostgreSQL, MariaDB, Oracle, SQL Server\n  Aurora (MySQL/PostgreSQL compatible, เร็วกว่า 5x)\n\nMulti-AZ:\n  Primary DB อยู่ AZ-1, Standby อยู่ AZ-2\n  ถ้า Primary ล่ม จะ failover ไป Standby อัตโนมัติ\n\nRead Replicas: กระจาย read traffic ลด load', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Service: RDS\nEngine: PostgreSQL 15\nInstance: db.t3.medium\nStorage: 100GB gp3\nMulti-AZ: enabled\nBackup: 7 days', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 10, title: 'AWS ECS', description: 'แสดง "Service: ECS", "Cluster: production", "Service: web-api", "Task Definition: web-api:5", "Desired: 3, Running: 3", "Launch Type: Fargate"', difficulty: 2, category: 'aws', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 ECS (Elastic Container Service) = รัน Docker containers บน AWS\n\nส่วนประกอบ:\n  Cluster = กลุ่มของ containers\n  Task Definition = blueprint ของ container (image, CPU, memory, ports)\n  Service = รักษาจำนวน tasks ที่ต้องการ\n  Task = instance ที่รันจริง\n\nLaunch Types:\n  EC2 = รันบน EC2 instances (จัดการเอง)\n  Fargate = serverless (AWS จัดการ infrastructure)\n\nFargate ง่ายกว่า แต่แพงกว่า\nEC2 ถูกกว่า แต่ต้องจัดการ instances เอง', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Service: ECS\nCluster: production\nService: web-api\nTask Definition: web-api:5\nDesired: 3, Running: 3\nLaunch Type: Fargate', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 11, title: 'AWS CloudFormation', description: 'แสดง "Service: CloudFormation", "Stack: my-infra", "Template: template.yaml", "Resources: 8", "Status: CREATE_COMPLETE"', difficulty: 2, category: 'aws', hint: 'echo 5 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 CloudFormation = Infrastructure as Code (IaC) ของ AWS\n\nเขียน template (YAML/JSON) กำหนด resources ทั้งหมด\nAWS สร้าง/อัพเดท/ลบ resources ให้อัตโนมัติ\n\nตัวอย่าง template:\n  AWSTemplateFormatVersion: "2010-09-09"\n  Resources:\n    MyBucket:\n      Type: AWS::S3::Bucket\n      Properties:\n        BucketName: my-app-bucket\n\nข้อดี:\n  - Repeatable (สร้างซ้ำได้เหมือนเดิม)\n  - Version controlled (เก็บใน Git)\n  - Rollback อัตโนมัติถ้า fail\n  - Drift detection (ตรวจจับการเปลี่ยนแปลง)', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Service: CloudFormation\nStack: my-infra\nTemplate: template.yaml\nResources: 8\nStatus: CREATE_COMPLETE', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 12, title: 'AWS Route53', description: 'แสดง "Service: Route53", "Domain: myapp.com", "Type: A Record", "Value: 54.210.30.40", "TTL: 300", "Health Check: healthy"', difficulty: 2, category: 'aws', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Route53 = DNS Service ของ AWS\n\nRecord Types:\n  A = ชี้ domain ไป IPv4\n  AAAA = ชี้ domain ไป IPv6\n  CNAME = ชี้ domain ไป domain อื่น\n  Alias = ชี้ไป AWS resources (ELB, S3, CloudFront)\n\nRouting Policies:\n  Simple = ชี้ไป 1 ที่\n  Weighted = แบ่ง traffic ตามน้ำหนัก\n  Latency = ชี้ไป region ที่เร็วที่สุด\n  Failover = สลับไป backup เมื่อ primary ล่ม\n  Geolocation = ชี้ตามตำแหน่งผู้ใช้', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Service: Route53\nDomain: myapp.com\nType: A Record\nValue: 54.210.30.40\nTTL: 300\nHealth Check: healthy', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 13, title: 'AWS ELB', description: 'แสดง "Service: ALB", "Name: web-alb", "Scheme: internet-facing", "Listeners: HTTP:80, HTTPS:443", "Target Group: 3 healthy targets", "Health Check: /health"', difficulty: 2, category: 'aws', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 ELB (Elastic Load Balancer) กระจาย traffic ไปหลาย targets\n\n3 ประเภท:\n  ALB (Application) = Layer 7 (HTTP/HTTPS)\n    - Path-based routing (/api -> backend, / -> frontend)\n    - Host-based routing (api.myapp.com -> backend)\n  NLB (Network) = Layer 4 (TCP/UDP)\n    - ประสิทธิภาพสูง, latency ต่ำ\n  CLB (Classic) = เก่า ไม่แนะนำ\n\nTarget Group = กลุ่ม instances ที่รับ traffic\nHealth Check = ตรวจสอบว่า target ยังทำงานอยู่', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Service: ALB\nName: web-alb\nScheme: internet-facing\nListeners: HTTP:80, HTTPS:443\nTarget Group: 3 healthy targets\nHealth Check: /health', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 14, title: 'AWS Auto Scaling', description: 'แสดง "Service: Auto Scaling", "Group: web-asg", "Min: 2, Max: 10, Desired: 3", "Policy: Target CPU 70%", "Scaling: +1 instance", "Cooldown: 300s"', difficulty: 3, category: 'aws', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Auto Scaling ปรับจำนวน EC2 อัตโนมัติตาม load\n\nส่วนประกอบ:\n  Launch Template = กำหนด spec ของ instance\n  Auto Scaling Group (ASG) = กลุ่ม instances\n    Min = จำนวนขั้นต่ำ\n    Max = จำนวนสูงสุด\n    Desired = จำนวนที่ต้องการ\n\nScaling Policies:\n  Target Tracking = รักษา metric ที่กำหนด (เช่น CPU 70%)\n  Step Scaling = เพิ่ม/ลดตามช่วง metric\n  Scheduled = ตั้งเวลาล่วงหน้า\n\nCooldown = เวลารอก่อน scale ครั้งถัดไป', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Service: Auto Scaling\nGroup: web-asg\nMin: 2, Max: 10, Desired: 3\nPolicy: Target CPU 70%\nScaling: +1 instance\nCooldown: 300s', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 15, title: 'AWS CloudWatch', description: 'แสดง "Service: CloudWatch", "Metric: CPUUtilization", "Value: 45.2%", "Alarm: HighCPU (threshold: 80%)", "State: OK", "Action: SNS notification"', difficulty: 2, category: 'aws', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 CloudWatch = Monitoring & Observability service\n\nส่วนประกอบ:\n  Metrics = ข้อมูลตัวเลข (CPU, Memory, Network)\n  Alarms = แจ้งเตือนเมื่อ metric เกิน threshold\n  Logs = เก็บ log จาก services ต่างๆ\n  Dashboards = แสดงผลกราฟ\n  Events/EventBridge = ตอบสนองต่อเหตุการณ์\n\nAlarm States:\n  OK = ปกติ\n  ALARM = เกิน threshold\n  INSUFFICIENT_DATA = ข้อมูลไม่พอ\n\nActions: ส่ง SNS, trigger Auto Scaling, Lambda', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Service: CloudWatch\nMetric: CPUUtilization\nValue: 45.2%\nAlarm: HighCPU (threshold: 80%)\nState: OK\nAction: SNS notification', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 16, title: 'AWS DynamoDB', description: 'แสดง "Service: DynamoDB", "Table: users", "Partition Key: userId", "Sort Key: createdAt", "RCU: 5, WCU: 5", "Mode: On-Demand"', difficulty: 2, category: 'aws', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 DynamoDB = NoSQL Database แบบ key-value/document\n\nคุณสมบัติ:\n  - Serverless (ไม่ต้องจัดการ server)\n  - Single-digit millisecond latency\n  - Auto scaling\n\nแนวคิด:\n  Table = ตาราง\n  Item = แถว (row)\n  Attribute = คอลัมน์\n  Partition Key = primary key\n  Sort Key = secondary key (optional)\n\nCapacity Modes:\n  On-Demand = จ่ายตามใช้ (เหมาะ traffic ไม่แน่นอน)\n  Provisioned = กำหนด RCU/WCU (ถูกกว่าถ้า traffic คงที่)', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Service: DynamoDB\nTable: users\nPartition Key: userId\nSort Key: createdAt\nRCU: 5, WCU: 5\nMode: On-Demand', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 17, title: 'AWS SQS & SNS', description: 'แสดง "SQS Queue: order-queue", "Type: Standard", "Messages: 150 in-flight", "SNS Topic: order-notifications", "Subscribers: 3 (email, lambda, sqs)"', difficulty: 2, category: 'aws', hint: 'echo 5 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 SQS & SNS = Messaging Services\n\nSQS (Simple Queue Service):\n  - Message Queue (ส่งข้อความระหว่าง services)\n  - Standard = ไม่รับประกันลำดับ, ส่งซ้ำได้\n  - FIFO = รับประกันลำดับ, ส่งครั้งเดียว\n  - Decouple services (ลด dependency)\n\nSNS (Simple Notification Service):\n  - Pub/Sub model (1 publisher, หลาย subscribers)\n  - Topic = ช่องทางส่งข้อความ\n  - Subscribers: Email, SMS, Lambda, SQS, HTTP\n\nPattern ที่นิยม: SNS -> SQS (fan-out)\nส่ง 1 message ไปหลาย queues พร้อมกัน', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'SQS Queue: order-queue\nType: Standard\nMessages: 150 in-flight\nSNS Topic: order-notifications\nSubscribers: 3 (email, lambda, sqs)', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 18, title: 'AWS CloudFront', description: 'แสดง "Service: CloudFront", "Distribution: d1234abc", "Origin: my-bucket.s3.amazonaws.com", "Price Class: PriceClass_100", "SSL: ACM certificate", "Cache Hit: 92%"', difficulty: 3, category: 'aws', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 CloudFront = CDN (Content Delivery Network)\n\nทำงาน:\n  1. User request เข้า Edge Location ใกล้ที่สุด\n  2. ถ้ามี cache -> ส่งกลับทันที (cache hit)\n  3. ถ้าไม่มี -> ดึงจาก Origin แล้ว cache ไว้\n\nOrigins:\n  S3 Bucket, ALB, EC2, Custom HTTP server\n\nPrice Classes:\n  PriceClass_All = ทุก Edge Locations\n  PriceClass_200 = ไม่รวม South America\n  PriceClass_100 = US, Canada, Europe เท่านั้น\n\nใช้กับ: Static websites, API acceleration, Video streaming', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Service: CloudFront\nDistribution: d1234abc\nOrigin: my-bucket.s3.amazonaws.com\nPrice Class: PriceClass_100\nSSL: ACM certificate\nCache Hit: 92%', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 19, title: 'AWS EKS', description: 'แสดง "Service: EKS", "Cluster: prod-cluster", "Version: 1.29", "Node Group: 3x t3.large", "Pods: 45 running", "Namespace: 4 (default, kube-system, app, monitoring)"', difficulty: 3, category: 'aws', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 EKS (Elastic Kubernetes Service) = Managed Kubernetes\n\nAWS จัดการ:\n  - Control Plane (API server, etcd, scheduler)\n  - HA across multiple AZs\n  - Security patches\n\nคุณจัดการ:\n  - Worker Nodes (EC2 หรือ Fargate)\n  - Applications & deployments\n  - Networking (VPC CNI plugin)\n\nNode Groups:\n  Managed = AWS จัดการ EC2 instances\n  Self-managed = จัดการเอง\n  Fargate = serverless (ไม่ต้องจัดการ nodes)\n\nเหมาะกับ: Microservices, CI/CD workloads, ML training', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Service: EKS\nCluster: prod-cluster\nVersion: 1.29\nNode Group: 3x t3.large\nPods: 45 running\nNamespace: 4 (default, kube-system, app, monitoring)', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 20, title: 'AWS Cost Optimization', description: 'แสดง "Monthly Cost Report:", "EC2: $450 (Reserved: save $200)", "S3: $25", "RDS: $180 (Multi-AZ)", "Lambda: $8", "Total: $663"', difficulty: 2, category: 'aws', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 AWS Cost Optimization\n\nเครื่องมือ:\n  Cost Explorer = วิเคราะห์ค่าใช้จ่าย\n  AWS Budgets = ตั้งงบประมาณ + แจ้งเตือน\n  Trusted Advisor = คำแนะนำลดค่าใช้จ่าย\n  Compute Optimizer = แนะนำ instance size\n\nวิธีประหยัด:\n  1. Right-sizing = ใช้ instance ขนาดเหมาะสม\n  2. Reserved Instances = จอง 1-3 ปี (ลด 30-60%)\n  3. Spot Instances = ประมูล (ลดสูงสุด 90%)\n  4. S3 Lifecycle = ย้ายข้อมูลเก่าไป Glacier\n  5. ปิด resources ที่ไม่ใช้ (dev/test นอกเวลา)', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Monthly Cost Report:\nEC2: $450 (Reserved: save $200)\nS3: $25\nRDS: $180 (Multi-AZ)\nLambda: $8\nTotal: $663', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 21, title: 'AWS Well-Architected', description: 'แสดง 6 pillars: "1. Operational Excellence", "2. Security", "3. Reliability", "4. Performance Efficiency", "5. Cost Optimization", "6. Sustainability"', difficulty: 3, category: 'aws', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 AWS Well-Architected Framework = แนวทางออกแบบระบบบน Cloud\n\n6 Pillars:\n  1. Operational Excellence = ดำเนินงานอย่างมีประสิทธิภาพ\n  2. Security = ปกป้องข้อมูลและระบบ\n  3. Reliability = ระบบทำงานได้ต่อเนื่อง\n  4. Performance Efficiency = ใช้ resources อย่างมีประสิทธิภาพ\n  5. Cost Optimization = ลดค่าใช้จ่ายที่ไม่จำเป็น\n  6. Sustainability = ลดผลกระทบต่อสิ่งแวดล้อม\n\nใช้ Well-Architected Tool ใน AWS Console เพื่อ review workload', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: '1. Operational Excellence\n2. Security\n3. Reliability\n4. Performance Efficiency\n5. Cost Optimization\n6. Sustainability', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 22, title: 'AWS Disaster Recovery', description: 'แสดง DR strategies: "1. Backup & Restore (RPO: hours)", "2. Pilot Light (RPO: minutes)", "3. Warm Standby (RPO: seconds)", "4. Multi-Site Active (RPO: near zero)"', difficulty: 3, category: 'aws', hint: 'echo 4 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Disaster Recovery (DR) = แผนกู้คืนระบบเมื่อเกิดภัยพิบัติ\n\nRPO = Recovery Point Objective (ข้อมูลหายได้กี่นาที)\nRTO = Recovery Time Objective (ระบบกลับมาใช้ได้ในกี่นาที)\n\n4 Strategies (เรียงจากถูก->แพง):\n  1. Backup & Restore = สำรองข้อมูล กู้คืนเมื่อจำเป็น\n  2. Pilot Light = รัน core services ขั้นต่ำ scale up เมื่อจำเป็น\n  3. Warm Standby = รัน scaled-down version ตลอด\n  4. Multi-Site Active = รัน full capacity ทั้ง 2 sites', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: '1. Backup & Restore (RPO: hours)\n2. Pilot Light (RPO: minutes)\n3. Warm Standby (RPO: seconds)\n4. Multi-Site Active (RPO: near zero)', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 23, title: 'AWS CI/CD Services', description: 'แสดง "CodeCommit: Git repository", "CodeBuild: Build & test", "CodeDeploy: Deploy to EC2/ECS/Lambda", "CodePipeline: Orchestrate CI/CD"', difficulty: 3, category: 'aws', hint: 'echo 4 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 AWS CI/CD Services\n\nCodeCommit = Git repository (เหมือน GitHub)\nCodeBuild = Build & test code (เหมือน GitHub Actions runner)\nCodeDeploy = Deploy ไป EC2, ECS, Lambda\nCodePipeline = เชื่อม source > build > deploy เป็น pipeline\n\nตัวอย่าง Pipeline:\n  Source (CodeCommit/GitHub)\n  -> Build (CodeBuild)\n  -> Test (CodeBuild)\n  -> Deploy Staging (CodeDeploy)\n  -> Manual Approval\n  -> Deploy Production (CodeDeploy)\n\nทางเลือก: ใช้ GitHub Actions หรือ Jenkins แทนได้', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'CodeCommit: Git repository\nCodeBuild: Build & test\nCodeDeploy: Deploy to EC2/ECS/Lambda\nCodePipeline: Orchestrate CI/CD', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 24, title: 'AWS Terraform', description: 'แสดง "Provider: aws", "Region: us-east-1", "Resources:", "  aws_vpc.main", "  aws_subnet.public", "  aws_instance.web"', difficulty: 3, category: 'aws', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Terraform กับ AWS = Infrastructure as Code (multi-cloud)\n\nตัวอย่าง:\n  provider "aws" {\n    region = "us-east-1"\n  }\n  resource "aws_instance" "web" {\n    ami           = "ami-0c55b159cbfafe1f0"\n    instance_type = "t3.micro"\n  }\n\nWorkflow:\n  terraform init    # ดาวน์โหลด AWS provider\n  terraform plan    # preview การเปลี่ยนแปลง\n  terraform apply   # สร้าง resources จริง\n  terraform destroy # ลบทุกอย่าง\n\nState file เก็บสถานะปัจจุบัน (ควรเก็บใน S3 + DynamoDB lock)', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Provider: aws\nRegion: us-east-1\nResources:\n  aws_vpc.main\n  aws_subnet.public\n  aws_instance.web', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 25, title: 'AWS Architecture Review', description: 'แสดง "Architecture: 3-Tier Web App", "Tier 1: CloudFront + S3 (frontend)", "Tier 2: ALB + ECS Fargate (API)", "Tier 3: RDS Multi-AZ (database)", "Extras: Route53, ACM, CloudWatch"', difficulty: 3, category: 'aws', hint: 'echo 5 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 AWS 3-Tier Architecture = รูปแบบที่นิยมที่สุด\n\nTier 1 - Presentation (Frontend):\n  CloudFront CDN + S3 static website\n\nTier 2 - Application (Backend):\n  ALB + ECS Fargate (หรือ EC2 Auto Scaling)\n  อยู่ใน Private Subnet\n\nTier 3 - Data (Database):\n  RDS Multi-AZ ใน Private Subnet\n  ElastiCache สำหรับ caching\n\nเสริม:\n  Route53 = DNS\n  ACM = SSL certificate\n  CloudWatch = monitoring\n  WAF = web application firewall', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Architecture: 3-Tier Web App\nTier 1: CloudFront + S3 (frontend)\nTier 2: ALB + ECS Fargate (API)\nTier 3: RDS Multi-AZ (database)\nExtras: Route53, ACM, CloudWatch', validationType: 'exact' },

  // === Azure (26-50) ===
  { id: 26, title: 'Azure คืออะไร', description: 'แสดง "Azure = Microsoft Cloud Platform", "Services: 200+", "Regions: 60+", "Compliance: 90+ certifications"', difficulty: 1, category: 'azure', hint: 'echo 4 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Microsoft Azure คือแพลตฟอร์ม Cloud Computing ของ Microsoft\n\nให้บริการ:\n  - Compute (VMs, App Service, Functions)\n  - Storage (Blob, Files, Queue)\n  - Database (SQL Database, Cosmos DB)\n  - AI/ML (Cognitive Services, OpenAI)\n  - DevOps (Azure DevOps, GitHub)\n\nข้อดี:\n  - รวมกับ Microsoft ecosystem (AD, Office 365, Teams)\n  - Hybrid cloud ดีเยี่ยม (Azure Arc, Stack)\n  - Enterprise-ready (compliance สูง)\n  - Free Tier: 12 เดือน + $200 credit', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Azure = Microsoft Cloud Platform\nServices: 200+\nRegions: 60+\nCompliance: 90+ certifications', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 27, title: 'Azure Resource Model', description: 'แสดง "Management Group: Contoso", "Subscription: Production", "Resource Group: rg-webapp-prod", "Resource: vm-web-01"', difficulty: 1, category: 'azure', hint: 'echo 4 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Azure Resource Hierarchy\n\nManagement Group (บริหารหลาย subscriptions)\n  └── Subscription (หน่วยเรียกเก็บเงิน)\n      └── Resource Group (กล่องรวม resources)\n          └── Resource (VM, Storage, DB...)\n\nResource Group:\n  - ทุก resource ต้องอยู่ใน RG\n  - ลบ RG = ลบทุก resource ข้างใน\n  - ใช้แยกตาม project/environment\n\nNaming Convention:\n  rg-{app}-{env} เช่น rg-webapp-prod\n  vm-{role}-{number} เช่น vm-web-01', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Management Group: Contoso\nSubscription: Production\nResource Group: rg-webapp-prod\nResource: vm-web-01', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 28, title: 'Azure AD & RBAC', description: 'แสดง "Azure AD Tenant: contoso.com", "User: admin@contoso.com", "Role: Contributor", "Scope: /subscriptions/xxx/resourceGroups/rg-prod", "MFA: enabled"', difficulty: 1, category: 'azure', hint: 'echo 5 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Azure AD (Entra ID) = Identity & Access Management\n\nAzure AD จัดการ:\n  - Users & Groups\n  - Authentication (MFA, SSO)\n  - Application registration\n\nRBAC (Role-Based Access Control):\n  Owner = full access + จัดการสิทธิ์\n  Contributor = full access (ยกเว้นจัดการสิทธิ์)\n  Reader = อ่านอย่างเดียว\n  Custom Roles = กำหนดเอง\n\nScope: Management Group > Subscription > Resource Group > Resource\nสิทธิ์ inherit จากบนลงล่าง', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Azure AD Tenant: contoso.com\nUser: admin@contoso.com\nRole: Contributor\nScope: /subscriptions/xxx/resourceGroups/rg-prod\nMFA: enabled', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 29, title: 'Azure Virtual Machines', description: 'แสดง "Service: Azure VM", "Name: vm-web-01", "Size: Standard_B2s", "OS: Ubuntu 22.04 LTS", "Disk: 64GB Premium SSD", "NSG: Allow HTTP, HTTPS, SSH"', difficulty: 1, category: 'azure', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Azure VM = Virtual Machine (เทียบเท่า AWS EC2)\n\nVM Sizes:\n  B-series = Burstable (dev/test)\n  D-series = General purpose\n  E-series = Memory optimized\n  F-series = Compute optimized\n  N-series = GPU\n\nDisks:\n  Standard HDD = ถูก, ช้า\n  Standard SSD = กลาง\n  Premium SSD = เร็ว\n  Ultra Disk = เร็วมาก (database)\n\nNSG (Network Security Group) = firewall rules\nAvailability Set/Zone = high availability', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Service: Azure VM\nName: vm-web-01\nSize: Standard_B2s\nOS: Ubuntu 22.04 LTS\nDisk: 64GB Premium SSD\nNSG: Allow HTTP, HTTPS, SSH', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 30, title: 'Azure Storage Account', description: 'แสดง "Service: Storage Account", "Name: stwebappprod001", "Kind: StorageV2", "Replication: LRS", "Tier: Hot", "Services: Blob, File, Queue, Table"', difficulty: 1, category: 'azure', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Azure Storage Account = ที่เก็บข้อมูลหลายรูปแบบ\n\n4 Services:\n  Blob Storage = object storage (เทียบเท่า S3)\n  File Storage = SMB file shares\n  Queue Storage = message queue\n  Table Storage = NoSQL key-value\n\nReplication:\n  LRS = 3 copies ใน 1 datacenter\n  ZRS = 3 copies ใน 3 zones\n  GRS = 6 copies ใน 2 regions\n  RA-GRS = GRS + read access จาก secondary\n\nAccess Tiers: Hot (เข้าถึงบ่อย), Cool (30 วัน+), Archive (180 วัน+)', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Service: Storage Account\nName: stwebappprod001\nKind: StorageV2\nReplication: LRS\nTier: Hot\nServices: Blob, File, Queue, Table', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 31, title: 'Azure App Service', description: 'แสดง "Service: App Service", "App: webapp-prod", "Plan: S1 (Standard)", "Runtime: Node.js 20 LTS", "URL: https://webapp-prod.azurewebsites.net", "Deployment: GitHub Actions"', difficulty: 2, category: 'azure', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 App Service = PaaS สำหรับ Web Apps (ไม่ต้องจัดการ server)\n\nรองรับ: .NET, Node.js, Python, Java, PHP, Ruby, Go\n\nApp Service Plans:\n  Free/Shared = ทดสอบ (shared infrastructure)\n  Basic (B1-B3) = dev/test (dedicated)\n  Standard (S1-S3) = production (auto-scale, slots)\n  Premium (P1-P3) = high performance\n\nDeployment Slots:\n  Production slot + Staging slot\n  Deploy ไป staging -> test -> swap เข้า production\n  ถ้ามีปัญหา swap กลับได้ทันที\n\nDeployment Methods: GitHub Actions, Azure DevOps, ZIP deploy, Docker', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Service: App Service\nApp: webapp-prod\nPlan: S1 (Standard)\nRuntime: Node.js 20 LTS\nURL: https://webapp-prod.azurewebsites.net\nDeployment: GitHub Actions', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 32, title: 'Azure SQL Database', description: 'แสดง "Service: Azure SQL", "Server: sql-prod-001", "Database: appdb", "Tier: General Purpose", "vCores: 2", "Backup: 7-day retention"', difficulty: 2, category: 'azure', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Azure SQL Database = Managed SQL Server\n\nPurchasing Models:\n  DTU = bundled compute+storage (ง่าย)\n  vCore = แยก compute/storage (ยืดหยุ่น)\n\nService Tiers:\n  Basic = dev/test (5 DTUs)\n  Standard = production ทั่วไป (10-3000 DTUs)\n  Premium = high I/O (125-4000 DTUs)\n  General Purpose = vCore model (production)\n  Business Critical = high availability\n  Hyperscale = ขนาดใหญ่มาก (100TB+)\n\nฟีเจอร์: Auto-tuning, Geo-replication, Point-in-time restore\nAzure SQL Managed Instance = ใกล้เคียง SQL Server on-prem มากที่สุด', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Service: Azure SQL\nServer: sql-prod-001\nDatabase: appdb\nTier: General Purpose\nvCores: 2\nBackup: 7-day retention', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 33, title: 'Azure AKS', description: 'แสดง "Service: AKS", "Cluster: aks-prod", "Version: 1.29.2", "Node Pool: 3x Standard_D4s_v3", "Pods: 52 running", "Ingress: NGINX + cert-manager"', difficulty: 3, category: 'azure', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 AKS (Azure Kubernetes Service) = Managed Kubernetes\n\nAzure จัดการ:\n  - Control Plane (ฟรี!)\n  - Upgrades & patches\n  - Monitoring integration\n\nNode Pools:\n  System pool = รัน K8s system pods\n  User pool = รัน application pods\n  สามารถมีหลาย pools ต่าง size ได้\n\nIntegrations:\n  Azure AD = RBAC authentication\n  Azure Monitor = Container Insights\n  Azure Policy = enforce standards\n  ACR = Azure Container Registry\n  Key Vault = secrets management\n\nNetworking: kubenet (basic) หรือ Azure CNI (advanced)', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Service: AKS\nCluster: aks-prod\nVersion: 1.29.2\nNode Pool: 3x Standard_D4s_v3\nPods: 52 running\nIngress: NGINX + cert-manager', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 34, title: 'Azure Functions', description: 'แสดง "Service: Azure Functions", "App: func-orderprocessor", "Runtime: Python 3.11", "Plan: Consumption", "Triggers: HTTP, Queue, Timer", "Executions: 15,000/day"', difficulty: 2, category: 'azure', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Azure Functions = Serverless compute (เทียบเท่า AWS Lambda)\n\nTriggers:\n  HTTP = เรียกผ่าน URL\n  Timer = ตั้งเวลา (cron expression)\n  Blob = เมื่อไฟล์เปลี่ยนใน Storage\n  Queue = เมื่อมี message ใน Queue Storage\n  Event Grid = เมื่อมี event\n  Cosmos DB = เมื่อข้อมูลเปลี่ยน\n\nHosting Plans:\n  Consumption = จ่ายตามใช้ (cold start)\n  Premium = pre-warmed instances (ไม่มี cold start)\n  Dedicated = รันบน App Service Plan\n\nDurable Functions = orchestrate หลาย functions เป็น workflow', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Service: Azure Functions\nApp: func-orderprocessor\nRuntime: Python 3.11\nPlan: Consumption\nTriggers: HTTP, Queue, Timer\nExecutions: 15,000/day', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 35, title: 'Azure Networking', description: 'แสดง "VNet: vnet-prod (10.0.0.0/16)", "Subnet-web: 10.0.1.0/24", "Subnet-app: 10.0.2.0/24", "Subnet-db: 10.0.3.0/24", "NSG: web-nsg (HTTP,HTTPS)", "LB: lb-web (Standard)"', difficulty: 2, category: 'azure', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Azure Networking\n\nVNet (Virtual Network) = เครือข่ายส่วนตัว (เทียบเท่า AWS VPC)\n\nส่วนประกอบ:\n  VNet = เครือข่ายหลัก\n  Subnet = แบ่งย่อย\n  NSG = Network Security Group (firewall)\n  Load Balancer = กระจาย traffic\n  Application Gateway = Layer 7 LB (เทียบเท่า ALB)\n  VPN Gateway = เชื่อม on-premises\n  ExpressRoute = dedicated connection\n  Azure Firewall = managed firewall\n\nVNet Peering = เชื่อม 2 VNets เข้าด้วยกัน\nService Endpoints = เข้าถึง Azure services ผ่าน private network', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'VNet: vnet-prod (10.0.0.0/16)\nSubnet-web: 10.0.1.0/24\nSubnet-app: 10.0.2.0/24\nSubnet-db: 10.0.3.0/24\nNSG: web-nsg (HTTP,HTTPS)\nLB: lb-web (Standard)', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 36, title: 'Azure Cosmos DB', description: 'แสดง "Service: Cosmos DB", "Account: cosmos-prod", "API: NoSQL", "Consistency: Session", "RU/s: 400", "Regions: East US, West Europe"', difficulty: 3, category: 'azure', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Cosmos DB = Globally distributed NoSQL database\n\nAPIs ที่รองรับ:\n  NoSQL (document) = native, แนะนำ\n  MongoDB = compatible กับ MongoDB\n  Cassandra = wide-column\n  Gremlin = graph database\n  Table = key-value\n\nConsistency Levels (เรียงจากแรง->อ่อน):\n  Strong > Bounded Staleness > Session > Consistent Prefix > Eventual\n\nRU/s (Request Units) = หน่วยวัด throughput\n  1 RU = อ่าน 1 document (1KB)\n\nGlobal Distribution: replicate ข้อมูลไปหลาย regions อัตโนมัติ', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Service: Cosmos DB\nAccount: cosmos-prod\nAPI: NoSQL\nConsistency: Session\nRU/s: 400\nRegions: East US, West Europe', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 37, title: 'Azure Monitor', description: 'แสดง "Service: Azure Monitor", "Metrics: CPU 42%, Memory 68%", "Log Analytics: 2.5GB/day", "Alert: High CPU > 80%", "Action Group: email + Teams", "Application Insights: enabled"', difficulty: 2, category: 'azure', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Azure Monitor = ระบบ monitoring ครบวงจร\n\nส่วนประกอบ:\n  Metrics = ข้อมูลตัวเลข real-time\n  Logs = Log Analytics workspace (KQL query)\n  Alerts = แจ้งเตือนตาม conditions\n  Action Groups = ช่องทางแจ้งเตือน (email, SMS, webhook)\n  Application Insights = APM สำหรับ web apps\n  Container Insights = monitoring สำหรับ AKS\n\nKQL (Kusto Query Language):\n  requests | where resultCode >= 500 | count\n  performanceCounters | where name == "% Processor Time"\n\nDashboards: สร้าง custom dashboard ใน Azure Portal', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Service: Azure Monitor\nMetrics: CPU 42%, Memory 68%\nLog Analytics: 2.5GB/day\nAlert: High CPU > 80%\nAction Group: email + Teams\nApplication Insights: enabled', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 38, title: 'Azure DevOps', description: 'แสดง "Service: Azure DevOps", "Project: MyWebApp", "Repos: 3 repositories", "Pipelines: CI + CD", "Boards: 15 work items", "Artifacts: npm feed"', difficulty: 2, category: 'azure', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Azure DevOps = ชุดเครื่องมือ DevOps ครบวงจร\n\n5 Services:\n  Azure Repos = Git repositories\n  Azure Pipelines = CI/CD (YAML-based)\n  Azure Boards = project management (Agile/Scrum)\n  Azure Artifacts = package management (npm, NuGet, Maven)\n  Azure Test Plans = manual/automated testing\n\nPipelines YAML:\n  trigger: [main]\n  pool:\n    vmImage: ubuntu-latest\n  steps:\n    - script: npm install\n    - script: npm test\n    - script: npm run build\n\nรองรับ: GitHub, Bitbucket, SVN นอกจาก Azure Repos', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Service: Azure DevOps\nProject: MyWebApp\nRepos: 3 repositories\nPipelines: CI + CD\nBoards: 15 work items\nArtifacts: npm feed', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 39, title: 'Azure Key Vault', description: 'แสดง "Service: Key Vault", "Vault: kv-prod-001", "Secrets: 12", "Keys: 3 (RSA-2048)", "Certificates: 2 (SSL)", "Access: RBAC enabled"', difficulty: 2, category: 'azure', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Azure Key Vault = จัดเก็บ secrets, keys, certificates อย่างปลอดภัย\n\n3 ประเภท:\n  Secrets = connection strings, passwords, API keys\n  Keys = encryption keys (RSA, EC)\n  Certificates = SSL/TLS certificates\n\nAccess Control:\n  Vault Access Policy = legacy\n  RBAC = แนะนำ (ใช้ Azure AD roles)\n\nIntegrations:\n  App Service = reference secrets โดยตรง\n  AKS = CSI driver mount secrets\n  Azure Functions = app settings reference\n  DevOps Pipelines = variable groups\n\nBest Practice: ไม่เก็บ secrets ใน code, ใช้ Key Vault เสมอ', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Service: Key Vault\nVault: kv-prod-001\nSecrets: 12\nKeys: 3 (RSA-2048)\nCertificates: 2 (SSL)\nAccess: RBAC enabled', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 40, title: 'Azure Container Registry', description: 'แสดง "Service: ACR", "Registry: acrprod001.azurecr.io", "SKU: Standard", "Images: 25", "Repositories: 8", "Geo-replication: enabled"', difficulty: 2, category: 'azure', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 ACR (Azure Container Registry) = Private Docker Registry\n\nSKUs:\n  Basic = dev/test (10GB)\n  Standard = production (100GB)\n  Premium = geo-replication, private link (500GB)\n\nใช้งาน:\n  az acr login --name acrprod001\n  docker tag myapp acrprod001.azurecr.io/myapp:v1\n  docker push acrprod001.azurecr.io/myapp:v1\n\nIntegrations:\n  AKS = pull images โดยตรง (managed identity)\n  App Service = deploy from ACR\n  Azure DevOps = build & push ใน pipeline\n\nTasks: ACR Tasks สร้าง image บน cloud (ไม่ต้อง docker locally)', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Service: ACR\nRegistry: acrprod001.azurecr.io\nSKU: Standard\nImages: 25\nRepositories: 8\nGeo-replication: enabled', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 41, title: 'Azure ARM Templates', description: 'แสดง "Service: ARM Templates", "Template: azuredeploy.json", "Parameters: 5", "Resources: 8", "Deployment: Incremental", "Status: Succeeded"', difficulty: 3, category: 'azure', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 ARM Templates = Infrastructure as Code ของ Azure (JSON)\n\nโครงสร้าง:\n  $schema, contentVersion\n  parameters = ค่าที่รับจากผู้ใช้\n  variables = ค่าคำนวณ\n  resources = สิ่งที่จะสร้าง\n  outputs = ค่าที่ส่งกลับ\n\nDeployment Modes:\n  Incremental = เพิ่ม/แก้ไข (ไม่ลบ)\n  Complete = ลบ resources ที่ไม่อยู่ใน template\n\nBicep = ภาษาใหม่แทน ARM JSON (อ่านง่ายกว่า)\n  resource storageAccount \"Microsoft.Storage/storageAccounts@2023-01-01\" = {\n    name: \"mystorage\"\n    location: resourceGroup().location\n    kind: \"StorageV2\"\n  }', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Service: ARM Templates\nTemplate: azuredeploy.json\nParameters: 5\nResources: 8\nDeployment: Incremental\nStatus: Succeeded', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 42, title: 'Azure Front Door', description: 'แสดง "Service: Azure Front Door", "Endpoint: myapp.azurefd.net", "Origins: East US + West Europe", "WAF: enabled", "Caching: 1 hour", "Health Probe: /health"', difficulty: 3, category: 'azure', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Azure Front Door = Global Load Balancer + CDN + WAF\n\nฟีเจอร์:\n  - Global HTTP load balancing\n  - SSL offloading\n  - URL-based routing\n  - Session affinity\n  - WAF (Web Application Firewall)\n  - DDoS protection\n  - Caching\n\nเทียบกับ AWS:\n  Front Door = CloudFront + ALB + WAF รวมกัน\n\nRouting Methods:\n  Latency = ส่งไป origin ที่เร็วที่สุด\n  Priority = primary/secondary\n  Weighted = แบ่งตามน้ำหนัก\n  Session Affinity = ส่งไป origin เดิม', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Service: Azure Front Door\nEndpoint: myapp.azurefd.net\nOrigins: East US + West Europe\nWAF: enabled\nCaching: 1 hour\nHealth Probe: /health', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 43, title: 'Azure Service Bus', description: 'แสดง "Service: Service Bus", "Namespace: sb-prod", "Queue: order-queue (1,250 msgs)", "Topic: notifications (3 subs)", "Tier: Standard", "Protocol: AMQP"', difficulty: 3, category: 'azure', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Azure Service Bus = Enterprise Message Broker\n\nQueue = point-to-point (1 sender -> 1 receiver)\nTopic = pub/sub (1 sender -> หลาย subscribers)\n\nเทียบกับ AWS:\n  Queue = SQS\n  Topic = SNS\n  Service Bus = SQS + SNS + advanced features\n\nAdvanced Features:\n  - Message sessions (ordered processing)\n  - Dead-letter queue (failed messages)\n  - Scheduled delivery\n  - Duplicate detection\n  - Transactions\n\nTiers: Basic (queues only), Standard (topics), Premium (dedicated)', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Service: Service Bus\nNamespace: sb-prod\nQueue: order-queue (1,250 msgs)\nTopic: notifications (3 subs)\nTier: Standard\nProtocol: AMQP', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 44, title: 'Azure Terraform', description: 'แสดง "Provider: azurerm", "Resource Group: rg-prod", "Resources:", "  azurerm_virtual_network.main", "  azurerm_subnet.web", "  azurerm_linux_virtual_machine.web"', difficulty: 3, category: 'azure', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Terraform กับ Azure\n\nProvider:\n  provider "azurerm" {\n    features {}\n  }\n\nAuthentication:\n  - Azure CLI (az login)\n  - Service Principal (CI/CD)\n  - Managed Identity (Azure VM/AKS)\n\nตัวอย่าง:\n  resource "azurerm_resource_group" "rg" {\n    name     = "rg-prod"\n    location = "eastus"\n  }\n\nState Backend:\n  Azure Storage Account (เก็บ state file)\n  terraform {\n    backend "azurerm" {\n      storage_account_name = "tfstate"\n      container_name       = "state"\n    }\n  }', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Provider: azurerm\nResource Group: rg-prod\nResources:\n  azurerm_virtual_network.main\n  azurerm_subnet.web\n  azurerm_linux_virtual_machine.web', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 45, title: 'Azure vs AWS Comparison', description: 'แสดง "Compute: EC2 = VM", "Storage: S3 = Blob Storage", "Database: RDS = Azure SQL", "Serverless: Lambda = Functions", "Container: ECS = Container Instances", "K8s: EKS = AKS"', difficulty: 2, category: 'azure', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Azure vs AWS Service Comparison\n\nCompute:\n  EC2 = Azure VM\n  Lambda = Azure Functions\n  ECS/Fargate = Container Instances/Apps\n  EKS = AKS\n\nStorage:\n  S3 = Blob Storage\n  EBS = Managed Disks\n  EFS = Azure Files\n\nDatabase:\n  RDS = Azure SQL / MySQL / PostgreSQL\n  DynamoDB = Cosmos DB\n  ElastiCache = Azure Cache for Redis\n\nNetworking:\n  VPC = VNet\n  ALB = Application Gateway\n  CloudFront = Front Door / CDN\n  Route53 = Azure DNS\n\nIaC: CloudFormation = ARM Templates / Bicep', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Compute: EC2 = VM\nStorage: S3 = Blob Storage\nDatabase: RDS = Azure SQL\nServerless: Lambda = Functions\nContainer: ECS = Container Instances\nK8s: EKS = AKS', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 46, title: 'Azure Security Center', description: 'แสดง "Service: Defender for Cloud", "Secure Score: 78/100", "Recommendations: 12", "Alerts: 2 (medium)", "Compliance: 85%", "Coverage: 95% resources"', difficulty: 3, category: 'azure', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Microsoft Defender for Cloud = Security posture management\n\nฟีเจอร์:\n  Secure Score = คะแนนความปลอดภัย (0-100)\n  Recommendations = คำแนะนำแก้ไข\n  Regulatory Compliance = ตรวจสอบตามมาตรฐาน\n  Security Alerts = แจ้งเตือนภัยคุกคาม\n\nDefender Plans:\n  Defender for Servers\n  Defender for Containers\n  Defender for SQL\n  Defender for Storage\n  Defender for Key Vault', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Service: Defender for Cloud\nSecure Score: 78/100\nRecommendations: 12\nAlerts: 2 (medium)\nCompliance: 85%\nCoverage: 95% resources', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 47, title: 'Azure Backup & DR', description: 'แสดง "Recovery Vault: vault-prod", "Backup Policy: Daily 2AM", "Retention: 30 days", "VM Backups: 5 protected", "Site Recovery: East US -> West US", "RPO: 15 minutes"', difficulty: 3, category: 'azure', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Azure Backup & Site Recovery\n\nAzure Backup:\n  - VM backup (full + incremental)\n  - SQL Database backup\n  - File share backup\n  - Blob backup\n  Recovery Vault เก็บ backup data\n\nAzure Site Recovery (ASR):\n  - DR สำหรับ VMs\n  - Replicate จาก Region A -> Region B\n  - Test failover ได้โดยไม่กระทบ production\n  - RPO ต่ำสุด 30 วินาที\n\nเทียบกับ AWS:\n  Backup = AWS Backup\n  Site Recovery = CloudEndure / DRS', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Recovery Vault: vault-prod\nBackup Policy: Daily 2AM\nRetention: 30 days\nVM Backups: 5 protected\nSite Recovery: East US -> West US\nRPO: 15 minutes', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 48, title: 'Azure Landing Zone', description: 'แสดง "Landing Zone: Enterprise-Scale", "Management Groups: 4", "Subscriptions: 6", "Policy Assignments: 25", "Blueprints: 3", "Hub-Spoke Network: configured"', difficulty: 3, category: 'azure', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Azure Landing Zone = โครงสร้างพื้นฐานสำหรับ enterprise\n\nEnterprise-Scale Architecture:\n  Management Groups\n    Platform (Identity, Management, Connectivity)\n    Landing Zones (Corp, Online)\n    Sandbox\n\nHub-Spoke Network:\n  Hub VNet = shared services (firewall, VPN, DNS)\n  Spoke VNets = workloads (peered กับ hub)\n\nAzure Policy = enforce standards อัตโนมัติ\n  เช่น: ห้ามสร้าง VM ใน region ที่ไม่อนุญาต\n\nBlueprints = template สำหรับ subscription ใหม่', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Landing Zone: Enterprise-Scale\nManagement Groups: 4\nSubscriptions: 6\nPolicy Assignments: 25\nBlueprints: 3\nHub-Spoke Network: configured', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 49, title: 'Azure Cost Management', description: 'แสดง "Monthly Budget: $5,000", "Current Spend: $3,250 (65%)", "Forecast: $4,800", "Top Service: AKS ($1,200)", "Savings: Reserved VMs (-$400)", "Alert: 80% threshold set"', difficulty: 2, category: 'azure', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Azure Cost Management\n\nเครื่องมือ:\n  Cost Analysis = วิเคราะห์ค่าใช้จ่าย\n  Budgets = ตั้งงบ + แจ้งเตือน\n  Advisor = คำแนะนำประหยัด\n  Reservations = จอง 1-3 ปี (ลด 30-60%)\n\nวิธีประหยัด:\n  1. Right-size VMs (Advisor แนะนำ)\n  2. Reserved Instances สำหรับ workload คงที่\n  3. Spot VMs สำหรับ batch jobs\n  4. Auto-shutdown dev/test VMs\n  5. Azure Hybrid Benefit (ใช้ license เดิม)\n  6. ใช้ PaaS แทน IaaS เมื่อทำได้', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Monthly Budget: $5,000\nCurrent Spend: $3,250 (65%)\nForecast: $4,800\nTop Service: AKS ($1,200)\nSavings: Reserved VMs (-$400)\nAlert: 80% threshold set', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 50, title: 'Azure Architecture Review', description: 'แสดง "Architecture: Microservices on AKS", "Frontend: Static Web App + CDN", "API: AKS + NGINX Ingress", "Database: Cosmos DB + Azure SQL", "Messaging: Service Bus", "Monitoring: App Insights + Grafana"', difficulty: 3, category: 'azure', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Azure Microservices Architecture\n\nFrontend:\n  Azure Static Web Apps หรือ Storage + CDN\n\nAPI Layer:\n  AKS (Kubernetes) หรือ Container Apps\n  API Management (gateway, rate limiting)\n\nData Layer:\n  Cosmos DB = NoSQL (global distribution)\n  Azure SQL = relational data\n  Azure Cache for Redis = caching\n\nMessaging:\n  Service Bus = reliable messaging\n  Event Grid = event-driven\n\nObservability:\n  Application Insights = APM\n  Log Analytics = centralized logs\n  Azure Monitor = metrics & alerts\n  Grafana = dashboards', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Architecture: Microservices on AKS\nFrontend: Static Web App + CDN\nAPI: AKS + NGINX Ingress\nDatabase: Cosmos DB + Azure SQL\nMessaging: Service Bus\nMonitoring: App Insights + Grafana', validationType: 'exact' },

  // === DevOps (51-75) ===
  { id: 51, title: 'DevOps คืออะไร', description: 'แสดง "DevOps = Development + Operations", "Goal: Faster, reliable delivery", "Culture: Collaboration", "Automation: CI/CD Pipeline", "Measurement: Metrics & Feedback"', difficulty: 1, category: 'devops', hint: 'echo 5 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 DevOps = วัฒนธรรมและแนวปฏิบัติที่รวม Development กับ Operations\n\nCALMS Framework:\n  Culture = ทำงานร่วมกัน ไม่โทษกัน\n  Automation = อัตโนมัติทุกอย่างที่ทำได้\n  Lean = ลดขั้นตอนที่ไม่จำเป็น\n  Measurement = วัดผลทุกอย่าง\n  Sharing = แบ่งปันความรู้\n\nDORA Metrics (วัดประสิทธิภาพ DevOps):\n  1. Deployment Frequency\n  2. Lead Time for Changes\n  3. Change Failure Rate\n  4. Time to Restore Service\n\nเป้าหมาย: Deploy บ่อยขึ้น เร็วขึ้น ปลอดภัยขึ้น', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'DevOps = Development + Operations\nGoal: Faster, reliable delivery\nCulture: Collaboration\nAutomation: CI/CD Pipeline\nMeasurement: Metrics & Feedback', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 52, title: 'Docker Fundamentals', description: 'แสดง "Docker: Container Runtime", "Image: Packaged application", "Container: Running instance", "Registry: Image storage", "Compose: Multi-container", "Volume: Persistent data"', difficulty: 1, category: 'devops', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Docker = Platform สำหรับ containerization\n\nแนวคิด:\n  Image = blueprint (read-only template)\n  Container = running instance ของ image\n  Dockerfile = สูตรสร้าง image\n  Registry = ที่เก็บ images (Docker Hub, ECR, ACR)\n\nทำไมใช้ Docker:\n  - "Works on my machine" หมดไป\n  - Consistent environment (dev = staging = prod)\n  - Lightweight กว่า VM\n  - เริ่มต้นเร็ว (วินาที vs นาที)\n  - Isolation ระหว่าง applications\n\nDocker vs VM:\n  Docker = share OS kernel (เบา)\n  VM = full OS per instance (หนัก)', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Docker: Container Runtime\nImage: Packaged application\nContainer: Running instance\nRegistry: Image storage\nCompose: Multi-container\nVolume: Persistent data', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 53, title: 'Dockerfile Deep Dive', description: 'แสดง "FROM node:20-alpine", "WORKDIR /app", "COPY package*.json ./", "RUN npm ci --production", "COPY . .", "EXPOSE 3000", "CMD [\"node\", \"server.js\"]"', difficulty: 2, category: 'devops', hint: 'echo 7 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Dockerfile Best Practices\n\nMulti-stage build (ลดขนาด image):\n  FROM node:20 AS builder\n  RUN npm run build\n  FROM node:20-alpine\n  COPY --from=builder /app/dist ./dist\n\nLayer Caching:\n  COPY package*.json ./ ก่อน COPY . .\n  เพราะ package.json เปลี่ยนไม่บ่อย = cache ได้\n\nSecurity:\n  - ใช้ alpine/slim images (เล็ก, ช่องโหว่น้อย)\n  - อย่ารัน root (USER node)\n  - ใช้ .dockerignore\n  - Scan images (Trivy, Snyk)\n\nCMD vs ENTRYPOINT:\n  CMD = default command (override ได้)\n  ENTRYPOINT = fixed command', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'FROM node:20-alpine\nWORKDIR /app\nCOPY package*.json ./\nRUN npm ci --production\nCOPY . .\nEXPOSE 3000\nCMD ["node", "server.js"]', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 54, title: 'Docker Compose', description: 'แสดง "services:", "  web: nginx:latest (port 80)", "  api: node:20 (port 3000)", "  db: postgres:16 (port 5432)", "  redis: redis:7 (port 6379)", "Status: 4 containers running"', difficulty: 2, category: 'devops', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Docker Compose = จัดการหลาย containers ด้วยไฟล์เดียว\n\ndocker-compose.yml:\n  services:\n    web:\n      image: nginx\n      ports: ["80:80"]\n      depends_on: [api]\n    api:\n      build: ./api\n      environment:\n        DB_HOST: db\n    db:\n      image: postgres:16\n      volumes:\n        - db-data:/var/lib/postgresql/data\n  volumes:\n    db-data:\n\nคำสั่ง:\n  docker compose up -d    # start\n  docker compose down      # stop + remove\n  docker compose logs -f   # ดู logs\n  docker compose ps        # ดู status', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'services:\n  web: nginx:latest (port 80)\n  api: node:20 (port 3000)\n  db: postgres:16 (port 5432)\n  redis: redis:7 (port 6379)\nStatus: 4 containers running', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 55, title: 'Kubernetes Architecture', description: 'แสดง "Control Plane:", "  API Server, etcd, Scheduler, Controller Manager", "Worker Nodes:", "  kubelet, kube-proxy, Container Runtime", "Objects:", "  Pod, Service, Deployment, ConfigMap, Secret"', difficulty: 2, category: 'devops', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Kubernetes (K8s) Architecture\n\nControl Plane (สมอง):\n  API Server = จุดเข้าถึง cluster (kubectl -> API Server)\n  etcd = database เก็บ state ทั้งหมด\n  Scheduler = เลือก node สำหรับ pod ใหม่\n  Controller Manager = รักษา desired state\n\nWorker Node (แรงงาน):\n  kubelet = agent บน node (รัน pods)\n  kube-proxy = จัดการ networking\n  Container Runtime = รัน containers (containerd)\n\nObjects:\n  Pod = หน่วยเล็กสุด (1+ containers)\n  Deployment = จัดการ pods + rolling updates\n  Service = expose pods (ClusterIP, NodePort, LoadBalancer)\n  ConfigMap/Secret = configuration data', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Control Plane:\n  API Server, etcd, Scheduler, Controller Manager\nWorker Nodes:\n  kubelet, kube-proxy, Container Runtime\nObjects:\n  Pod, Service, Deployment, ConfigMap, Secret', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 56, title: 'K8s Deployments', description: 'แสดง "Deployment: web-app", "Replicas: 3/3 ready", "Strategy: RollingUpdate", "Max Surge: 1", "Max Unavailable: 0", "Image: myapp:v2.1.0"', difficulty: 2, category: 'devops', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Kubernetes Deployment จัดการ Pod lifecycle\n\nYAML:\n  apiVersion: apps/v1\n  kind: Deployment\n  spec:\n    replicas: 3\n    strategy:\n      type: RollingUpdate\n      rollingUpdate:\n        maxSurge: 1\n        maxUnavailable: 0\n\nUpdate Strategies:\n  RollingUpdate = อัพเดททีละตัว (zero downtime)\n    maxSurge = สร้างเกินได้กี่ตัว\n    maxUnavailable = หายได้กี่ตัว\n  Recreate = ลบทั้งหมดแล้วสร้างใหม่ (มี downtime)\n\nRollback:\n  kubectl rollout undo deployment/web-app\n  kubectl rollout history deployment/web-app', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Deployment: web-app\nReplicas: 3/3 ready\nStrategy: RollingUpdate\nMax Surge: 1\nMax Unavailable: 0\nImage: myapp:v2.1.0', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 57, title: 'K8s Services & Ingress', description: 'แสดง "ClusterIP: internal only", "NodePort: node:30080", "LoadBalancer: external LB", "Ingress: myapp.com -> web-svc:80", "Ingress: api.myapp.com -> api-svc:3000", "TLS: cert-manager (Lets Encrypt)"', difficulty: 2, category: 'devops', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 K8s Networking: Service & Ingress\n\nService Types:\n  ClusterIP = ภายใน cluster (default)\n  NodePort = เปิด port บน node (30000-32767)\n  LoadBalancer = สร้าง cloud LB\n  ExternalName = DNS alias\n\nIngress = HTTP routing rules\n  - Path-based: /api -> api-svc, / -> web-svc\n  - Host-based: api.myapp.com -> api-svc\n  - TLS termination\n\nIngress Controllers:\n  NGINX Ingress = ยอดนิยม\n  Traefik = auto-discovery\n  AWS ALB Ingress = ใช้ ALB\n\ncert-manager = จัดการ SSL certificates อัตโนมัติ (Let us Encrypt)', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'ClusterIP: internal only\nNodePort: node:30080\nLoadBalancer: external LB\nIngress: myapp.com -> web-svc:80\nIngress: api.myapp.com -> api-svc:3000\nTLS: cert-manager (Lets Encrypt)', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 58, title: 'Helm Package Manager', description: 'แสดง "Helm: K8s Package Manager", "Chart: my-app (0.2.0)", "Release: production", "Values: replicas=3, image=v2.1", "Repo: https://charts.myorg.com", "Status: deployed"', difficulty: 2, category: 'devops', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Helm = Package Manager สำหรับ Kubernetes\n\nChart = ชุด K8s manifests ที่ template ได้\n\nโครงสร้าง Chart:\n  my-chart/\n    Chart.yaml      # metadata\n    values.yaml     # default values\n    templates/      # K8s manifests\n      deployment.yaml\n      service.yaml\n\nTemplate:\n  replicas: {{ .Values.replicas }}\n  image: {{ .Values.image.tag }}\n\nคำสั่ง:\n  helm install prod ./my-chart -f prod-values.yaml\n  helm upgrade prod ./my-chart\n  helm rollback prod 1\n  helm list\n  helm uninstall prod', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Helm: K8s Package Manager\nChart: my-app (0.2.0)\nRelease: production\nValues: replicas=3, image=v2.1\nRepo: https://charts.myorg.com\nStatus: deployed', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 59, title: 'Terraform Fundamentals', description: 'แสดง "Terraform: Infrastructure as Code", "Language: HCL", "Providers: AWS, Azure, GCP, K8s", "State: terraform.tfstate", "Workflow: init > plan > apply", "Backend: S3 + DynamoDB"', difficulty: 2, category: 'devops', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Terraform = Multi-cloud Infrastructure as Code\n\nHCL (HashiCorp Configuration Language):\n  resource "aws_instance" "web" {\n    ami           = "ami-xxx"\n    instance_type = "t3.micro"\n    tags = { Name = "web-server" }\n  }\n\nWorkflow:\n  terraform init    # ดาวน์โหลด providers\n  terraform plan    # preview changes\n  terraform apply   # create resources\n  terraform destroy # delete all\n\nState Management:\n  Local = terraform.tfstate (ไม่เหมาะ team)\n  Remote = S3/Azure Storage (แนะนำ)\n  State Lock = DynamoDB/Blob lease (ป้องกัน conflict)\n\nModules = reusable components', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Terraform: Infrastructure as Code\nLanguage: HCL\nProviders: AWS, Azure, GCP, K8s\nState: terraform.tfstate\nWorkflow: init > plan > apply\nBackend: S3 + DynamoDB', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 60, title: 'CI/CD Pipeline Design', description: 'แสดง "Stage 1: Source (Git push)", "Stage 2: Build (Docker build)", "Stage 3: Test (unit + integration)", "Stage 4: Security (scan + SAST)", "Stage 5: Deploy Staging", "Stage 6: Deploy Production"', difficulty: 2, category: 'devops', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 CI/CD Pipeline = อัตโนมัติตั้งแต่ code ถึง production\n\nCI (Continuous Integration):\n  1. Developer push code\n  2. Build application\n  3. Run unit tests\n  4. Code quality check (linting)\n  5. Security scan (SAST, dependency check)\n\nCD (Continuous Delivery):\n  6. Deploy to staging\n  7. Run integration tests\n  8. Manual approval (optional)\n  9. Deploy to production\n  10. Smoke tests\n\nTools:\n  GitHub Actions, GitLab CI, Jenkins, Azure Pipelines\n  ArgoCD (GitOps-based CD)\n\nBest Practice: ทุก commit ต้องผ่าน pipeline', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Stage 1: Source (Git push)\nStage 2: Build (Docker build)\nStage 3: Test (unit + integration)\nStage 4: Security (scan + SAST)\nStage 5: Deploy Staging\nStage 6: Deploy Production', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 61, title: 'GitHub Actions', description: 'แสดง "Platform: GitHub Actions", "Trigger: push to main", "Runner: ubuntu-latest", "Steps: checkout, build, test, deploy", "Secrets: DOCKER_TOKEN", "Status: success"', difficulty: 2, category: 'devops', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 GitHub Actions = CI/CD ใน GitHub\n\nWorkflow (.github/workflows/ci.yml):\n  name: CI\n  on:\n    push:\n      branches: [main]\n  jobs:\n    build:\n      runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n      steps:\n        - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n        - run: npm install\n        - run: npm test\n        - run: docker build -t myapp .\n\nFeatures:\n  - Matrix builds (test หลาย versions)\n  - Secrets management\n  - Reusable workflows\n  - Self-hosted runners\n  - Marketplace (1000+ actions)\n\nFree: 2,000 minutes/month (public repos unlimited)', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Platform: GitHub Actions\nTrigger: push to main\nRunner: ubuntu-latest\nSteps: checkout, build, test, deploy\nSecrets: DOCKER_TOKEN\nStatus: success', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 62, title: 'Monitoring & Observability', description: 'แสดง "Metrics: Prometheus + Grafana", "Logs: ELK Stack / Loki", "Traces: Jaeger / Tempo", "Alerts: PagerDuty / OpsGenie", "SLO: 99.9% availability", "Error Budget: 43 minutes/month"', difficulty: 3, category: 'devops', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Observability = เข้าใจระบบจากข้อมูลที่ระบบส่งออกมา\n\n3 Pillars:\n  Metrics = ตัวเลข (CPU, latency, error rate)\n    Tools: Prometheus, CloudWatch, Datadog\n  Logs = เหตุการณ์ที่เกิดขึ้น\n    Tools: ELK Stack, Loki, CloudWatch Logs\n  Traces = ติดตาม request ข้าม services\n    Tools: Jaeger, Zipkin, X-Ray\n\nSLI/SLO/SLA:\n  SLI = ตัวชี้วัด (เช่น latency p99)\n  SLO = เป้าหมาย (เช่น 99.9% availability)\n  SLA = สัญญากับลูกค้า\n  Error Budget = เวลาที่ระบบล่มได้ (99.9% = 43 min/month)', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Metrics: Prometheus + Grafana\nLogs: ELK Stack / Loki\nTraces: Jaeger / Tempo\nAlerts: PagerDuty / OpsGenie\nSLO: 99.9% availability\nError Budget: 43 minutes/month', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 63, title: 'Infrastructure Security', description: 'แสดง "Network: Zero Trust", "Secrets: Vault / Key Vault", "Scanning: Trivy + Snyk", "Policy: OPA / Kyverno", "Compliance: SOC2, ISO27001", "Encryption: TLS 1.3 + AES-256"', difficulty: 3, category: 'devops', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 DevSecOps = Security ในทุกขั้นตอนของ DevOps\n\nShift Left = ตรวจสอบ security ตั้งแต่เริ่ม\n\nCode:\n  SAST = Static Application Security Testing\n  SCA = Software Composition Analysis (dependencies)\n\nBuild:\n  Image scanning (Trivy, Snyk)\n  Base image hardening\n\nDeploy:\n  Policy as Code (OPA, Kyverno)\n  Network Policies\n  Pod Security Standards\n\nRuntime:\n  Zero Trust networking\n  Secrets management (Vault, Key Vault)\n  Runtime security (Falco)\n\nEncryption: at rest (AES-256) + in transit (TLS 1.3)', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Network: Zero Trust\nSecrets: Vault / Key Vault\nScanning: Trivy + Snyk\nPolicy: OPA / Kyverno\nCompliance: SOC2, ISO27001\nEncryption: TLS 1.3 + AES-256', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 64, title: 'K8s ConfigMaps & Secrets', description: 'แสดง "ConfigMap: app-config", "  APP_ENV=production", "  LOG_LEVEL=info", "Secret: db-credentials", "  DB_USER=admin (base64)", "  DB_PASS=*** (base64)"', difficulty: 2, category: 'devops', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 ConfigMap & Secret = จัดการ configuration ใน K8s\n\nConfigMap = ข้อมูลทั่วไป (ไม่ลับ)\n  kubectl create configmap app-config --from-literal=APP_ENV=production\n\nSecret = ข้อมูลลับ (base64 encoded)\n  kubectl create secret generic db-creds --from-literal=DB_PASS=mypass\n\nใช้งานใน Pod:\n  envFrom:\n    - configMapRef: { name: app-config }\n    - secretRef: { name: db-creds }\n\nหรือ mount เป็น file:\n  volumes:\n    - name: config\n      configMap: { name: app-config }\n\nข้อควรระวัง: Secret เป็นแค่ base64 ไม่ได้เข้ารหัส! ใช้ Sealed Secrets หรือ External Secrets', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'ConfigMap: app-config\n  APP_ENV=production\n  LOG_LEVEL=info\nSecret: db-credentials\n  DB_USER=admin (base64)\n  DB_PASS=*** (base64)', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 65, title: 'K8s Namespaces & RBAC', description: 'แสดง "Namespaces: default, production, staging, monitoring", "Role: developer (pods: get,list,watch)", "RoleBinding: dev-team -> developer", "ServiceAccount: app-sa", "ClusterRole: cluster-admin"', difficulty: 3, category: 'devops', hint: 'echo 5 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 K8s Namespaces & RBAC\n\nNamespace = แบ่ง cluster เป็นส่วนๆ\n  - แยก environments (dev, staging, prod)\n  - Resource quotas per namespace\n  - Network policies per namespace\n\nRBAC (Role-Based Access Control):\n  Role = สิทธิ์ภายใน namespace\n  ClusterRole = สิทธิ์ทั้ง cluster\n  RoleBinding = ผูก Role กับ User/Group\n  ClusterRoleBinding = ผูก ClusterRole\n\nServiceAccount = identity สำหรับ pods\n  ใช้เข้าถึง K8s API หรือ cloud resources', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Namespaces: default, production, staging, monitoring\nRole: developer (pods: get,list,watch)\nRoleBinding: dev-team -> developer\nServiceAccount: app-sa\nClusterRole: cluster-admin', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 66, title: 'K8s Storage', description: 'แสดง "PV: pv-data (100Gi, ReadWriteOnce)", "PVC: pvc-data (bound to pv-data)", "StorageClass: gp3 (aws-ebs-csi)", "StatefulSet: database (3 replicas)", "VolumeSnapshot: snap-20240101", "Backup: Velero (daily)"', difficulty: 3, category: 'devops', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Kubernetes Storage\n\nPersistentVolume (PV) = storage resource\nPersistentVolumeClaim (PVC) = request for storage\nStorageClass = dynamic provisioning\n\nAccess Modes:\n  ReadWriteOnce (RWO) = 1 node อ่าน/เขียน\n  ReadOnlyMany (ROX) = หลาย nodes อ่าน\n  ReadWriteMany (RWX) = หลาย nodes อ่าน/เขียน\n\nStatefulSet = สำหรับ stateful apps (database)\n  - Stable network identity (pod-0, pod-1)\n  - Ordered deployment/scaling\n  - Persistent storage per pod\n\nBackup: Velero = backup K8s resources + volumes', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'PV: pv-data (100Gi, ReadWriteOnce)\nPVC: pvc-data (bound to pv-data)\nStorageClass: gp3 (aws-ebs-csi)\nStatefulSet: database (3 replicas)\nVolumeSnapshot: snap-20240101\nBackup: Velero (daily)', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 67, title: 'Terraform Modules', description: 'แสดง "Module: vpc", "  Source: ./modules/vpc", "  Variables: cidr, azs, name", "Module: eks", "  Source: terraform-aws-modules/eks/aws", "  Variables: cluster_name, node_groups"', difficulty: 3, category: 'devops', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Terraform Modules = Reusable infrastructure components\n\nLocal Module:\n  module "vpc" {\n    source = "./modules/vpc"\n    cidr   = "10.0.0.0/16"\n    name   = "prod-vpc"\n  }\n\nRegistry Module:\n  module "eks" {\n    source  = "terraform-aws-modules/eks/aws"\n    version = "~> 19.0"\n    cluster_name = "prod"\n  }\n\nModule Structure:\n  modules/vpc/\n    main.tf      # resources\n    variables.tf # inputs\n    outputs.tf   # outputs\n\nBest Practice:\n  - DRY (Don not Repeat Yourself)\n  - Version pin modules\n  - ใช้ outputs เชื่อม modules', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Module: vpc\n  Source: ./modules/vpc\n  Variables: cidr, azs, name\nModule: eks\n  Source: terraform-aws-modules/eks/aws\n  Variables: cluster_name, node_groups', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 68, title: 'Container Orchestration Patterns', description: 'แสดง "Sidecar: log collector", "Ambassador: API proxy", "Adapter: format converter", "Init Container: db migration", "Job: batch processing", "CronJob: daily cleanup"', difficulty: 3, category: 'devops', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 K8s Design Patterns\n\nMulti-container Patterns:\n  Sidecar = helper container (logging, monitoring)\n  Ambassador = proxy container (service mesh)\n  Adapter = transform output format\n\nInit Containers:\n  รันก่อน main container\n  ใช้สำหรับ: db migration, config download, wait for dependency\n\nWorkload Types:\n  Deployment = stateless apps (web, API)\n  StatefulSet = stateful apps (database)\n  DaemonSet = รันบนทุก node (monitoring agent)\n  Job = รันครั้งเดียว (batch processing)\n  CronJob = รันตามเวลา (cleanup, backup)', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Sidecar: log collector\nAmbassador: API proxy\nAdapter: format converter\nInit Container: db migration\nJob: batch processing\nCronJob: daily cleanup', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 69, title: 'Service Mesh', description: 'แสดง "Service Mesh: Istio", "Sidecar: Envoy proxy", "Features: mTLS, traffic management", "Observability: distributed tracing", "Policy: rate limiting, circuit breaker", "Gateway: ingress + egress"', difficulty: 3, category: 'devops', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Service Mesh = infrastructure layer สำหรับ service-to-service communication\n\nปัญหาที่แก้:\n  - Service discovery\n  - Load balancing\n  - Encryption (mTLS)\n  - Observability\n  - Traffic management\n\nIstio (ยอดนิยม):\n  Envoy sidecar proxy inject เข้าทุก pod\n  Control plane จัดการ configuration\n\nTraffic Management:\n  Canary deployment (90/10 traffic split)\n  A/B testing\n  Circuit breaker\n  Retry + timeout\n\nAlternatives: Linkerd (เบากว่า), Consul Connect', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Service Mesh: Istio\nSidecar: Envoy proxy\nFeatures: mTLS, traffic management\nObservability: distributed tracing\nPolicy: rate limiting, circuit breaker\nGateway: ingress + egress', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 70, title: 'Microservices Architecture', description: 'แสดง "Pattern: Microservices", "Services: user, order, payment, notification", "Communication: REST + gRPC + Events", "Database: Database per service", "API Gateway: Kong / Envoy", "Discovery: K8s DNS / Consul"', difficulty: 3, category: 'devops', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Microservices = แยก application เป็น services เล็กๆ อิสระ\n\nหลักการ:\n  - Single Responsibility (1 service = 1 หน้าที่)\n  - Database per Service (แยก data)\n  - API-first design\n  - Independent deployment\n\nCommunication:\n  Synchronous: REST, gRPC\n  Asynchronous: Message Queue (SQS, RabbitMQ, Kafka)\n\nPatterns:\n  API Gateway = single entry point\n  Circuit Breaker = ป้องกัน cascading failure\n  Saga = distributed transactions\n  CQRS = แยก read/write\n  Event Sourcing = เก็บ events แทน state\n\nข้อเสีย: complexity, network latency, debugging ยาก', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Pattern: Microservices\nServices: user, order, payment, notification\nCommunication: REST + gRPC + Events\nDatabase: Database per service\nAPI Gateway: Kong / Envoy\nDiscovery: K8s DNS / Consul', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 71, title: 'Platform Engineering', description: 'แสดง "Internal Developer Platform (IDP)", "Self-service: deploy in minutes", "Templates: Backstage + Cookiecutter", "Golden Paths: standardized workflows", "Metrics: DORA + SPACE", "Tools: Backstage, Port, Humanitec"', difficulty: 3, category: 'devops', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Platform Engineering = สร้าง Internal Developer Platform\n\nเป้าหมาย: ลด cognitive load ของ developers\n\nIDP (Internal Developer Platform):\n  - Self-service infrastructure\n  - Standardized templates\n  - Automated workflows\n  - Built-in best practices\n\nGolden Paths:\n  เส้นทางมาตรฐานที่แนะนำ (ไม่บังคับ)\n  เช่น: สร้าง service ใหม่ -> template -> CI/CD -> monitoring\n\nBackstage (Spotify):\n  - Service catalog\n  - Software templates\n  - TechDocs\n  - Plugin ecosystem\n\nวัดผล: DORA metrics + Developer satisfaction', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Internal Developer Platform (IDP)\nSelf-service: deploy in minutes\nTemplates: Backstage + Cookiecutter\nGolden Paths: standardized workflows\nMetrics: DORA + SPACE\nTools: Backstage, Port, Humanitec', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 72, title: 'Terraform Workspaces', description: 'แสดง "Workspace: production", "State: s3://tf-state/prod/terraform.tfstate", "Variables: instance_type=t3.large", "Workspace: staging", "State: s3://tf-state/staging/terraform.tfstate", "Variables: instance_type=t3.small"', difficulty: 3, category: 'devops', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Terraform Workspaces = จัดการหลาย environments\n\nวิธีที่ 1: Workspaces\n  terraform workspace new staging\n  terraform workspace select production\n  ใช้ terraform.workspace ใน code\n\nวิธีที่ 2: Directory Structure (แนะนำ)\n  environments/\n    production/\n      main.tf\n      terraform.tfvars\n    staging/\n      main.tf\n      terraform.tfvars\n  modules/\n    vpc/\n    eks/\n\nRemote State:\n  backend "s3" {\n    bucket = "tf-state"\n    key    = "prod/terraform.tfstate"\n    dynamodb_table = "tf-lock"\n  }', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Workspace: production\nState: s3://tf-state/prod/terraform.tfstate\nVariables: instance_type=t3.large\nWorkspace: staging\nState: s3://tf-state/staging/terraform.tfstate\nVariables: instance_type=t3.small', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 73, title: 'K8s HPA & VPA', description: 'แสดง "HPA: web-app", "  Min: 2, Max: 10, Current: 4", "  Target: CPU 70% (current: 65%)", "VPA: api-server", "  Mode: Auto", "  Recommendation: 500m CPU, 512Mi Memory"', difficulty: 3, category: 'devops', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 K8s Auto Scaling\n\nHPA (Horizontal Pod Autoscaler):\n  เพิ่ม/ลดจำนวน pods ตาม metrics\n  apiVersion: autoscaling/v2\n  spec:\n    minReplicas: 2\n    maxReplicas: 10\n    metrics:\n    - type: Resource\n      resource:\n        name: cpu\n        target: { averageUtilization: 70 }\n\nVPA (Vertical Pod Autoscaler):\n  ปรับ CPU/Memory requests ของ pods\n  Modes: Off (แนะนำ), Auto (ปรับเอง)\n\nCluster Autoscaler:\n  เพิ่ม/ลด nodes เมื่อ pods ไม่มีที่รัน\n\nKEDA = event-driven autoscaling (scale to zero)', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'HPA: web-app\n  Min: 2, Max: 10, Current: 4\n  Target: CPU 70% (current: 65%)\nVPA: api-server\n  Mode: Auto\n  Recommendation: 500m CPU, 512Mi Memory', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 74, title: 'GitOps with Terraform', description: 'แสดง "Atlantis: Terraform PR automation", "PR opened: terraform plan", "PR approved: terraform apply", "State: locked during apply", "Drift: detected and alerted", "Policy: OPA/Sentinel checks"', difficulty: 3, category: 'devops', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 GitOps for Infrastructure (Terraform)\n\nAtlantis = Terraform PR automation\n  1. Developer สร้าง PR แก้ไข .tf files\n  2. Atlantis รัน terraform plan อัตโนมัติ\n  3. แสดง plan ใน PR comment\n  4. Reviewer approve\n  5. Atlantis รัน terraform apply\n\nPolicy as Code:\n  OPA (Open Policy Agent) = general purpose\n  Sentinel (HashiCorp) = Terraform specific\n  เช่น: ห้ามสร้าง public S3 bucket\n\nDrift Detection:\n  terraform plan ตรวจจับ manual changes\n  แจ้งเตือนเมื่อ state ไม่ตรงกับ reality', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Atlantis: Terraform PR automation\nPR opened: terraform plan\nPR approved: terraform apply\nState: locked during apply\nDrift: detected and alerted\nPolicy: OPA/Sentinel checks', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 75, title: 'DevOps Architecture Review', description: 'แสดง "Source: GitHub (trunk-based)", "CI: GitHub Actions (build+test+scan)", "Registry: ECR / ACR", "CD: ArgoCD (GitOps)", "Infra: Terraform + Atlantis", "Monitor: Prometheus + Grafana + Loki"', difficulty: 3, category: 'devops', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Modern DevOps Architecture\n\nSource Control:\n  GitHub/GitLab + trunk-based development\n  Feature branches + PR reviews\n\nCI Pipeline:\n  GitHub Actions / GitLab CI\n  Build > Test > Scan > Push image\n\nCD Pipeline:\n  ArgoCD (GitOps) = watch Git, sync to K8s\n  Canary/Blue-Green deployments\n\nInfrastructure:\n  Terraform + Atlantis (PR-based)\n  Modules for reusability\n\nObservability:\n  Prometheus + Grafana (metrics)\n  Loki (logs)\n  Tempo (traces)\n  PagerDuty (alerting)\n\nSecurity: Trivy, OPA, Sealed Secrets, cert-manager', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Source: GitHub (trunk-based)\nCI: GitHub Actions (build+test+scan)\nRegistry: ECR / ACR\nCD: ArgoCD (GitOps)\nInfra: Terraform + Atlantis\nMonitor: Prometheus + Grafana + Loki', validationType: 'exact' },

  // === GitOps (76-90) ===
  { id: 76, title: 'GitOps คืออะไร', description: 'แสดง "GitOps = Git as Single Source of Truth", "Declarative: desired state in Git", "Automated: reconciliation loop", "Observable: drift detection", "Auditable: Git history = audit log"', difficulty: 1, category: 'gitops', hint: 'echo 5 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 GitOps = ใช้ Git เป็นศูนย์กลางจัดการ infrastructure และ applications\n\nหลักการ:\n  1. Declarative = ประกาศสถานะที่ต้องการ (ไม่ใช่ขั้นตอน)\n  2. Versioned = ทุกอย่างอยู่ใน Git\n  3. Automated = agent ดึงจาก Git แล้ว apply อัตโนมัติ\n  4. Self-healing = ตรวจจับ drift แล้วแก้ไข\n\nPush vs Pull:\n  Push (CI/CD แบบเดิม): pipeline push ไป cluster\n  Pull (GitOps): agent ใน cluster pull จาก Git\n\nข้อดี Pull model:\n  - ไม่ต้องให้ CI access cluster\n  - Cluster reconcile ตัวเอง\n  - Git history = audit trail\n  - Rollback = git revert', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'GitOps = Git as Single Source of Truth\nDeclarative: desired state in Git\nAutomated: reconciliation loop\nObservable: drift detection\nAuditable: Git history = audit log', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 77, title: 'Git Branching Strategies', description: 'แสดง "Git Flow: main, develop, feature/*, release/*, hotfix/*", "GitHub Flow: main + feature branches", "Trunk-Based: main + short-lived branches", "GitOps Recommended: Trunk-Based", "Environment branches: main=prod, staging, dev"', difficulty: 1, category: 'gitops', hint: 'echo 5 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Git Branching Strategies\n\nGit Flow:\n  main = production\n  develop = integration\n  feature/* = new features\n  release/* = prepare release\n  hotfix/* = urgent fixes\n  ข้อเสีย: ซับซ้อน, merge conflicts\n\nGitHub Flow:\n  main + short-lived feature branches\n  PR -> review -> merge -> deploy\n  เรียบง่าย เหมาะกับ CI/CD\n\nTrunk-Based Development:\n  ทุกคน commit เข้า main บ่อยๆ\n  Feature flags แทน long-lived branches\n  แนะนำสำหรับ GitOps\n\nGitOps repo strategy:\n  App repo = source code\n  Config repo = K8s manifests (แยก repo)', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Git Flow: main, develop, feature/*, release/*, hotfix/*\nGitHub Flow: main + feature branches\nTrunk-Based: main + short-lived branches\nGitOps Recommended: Trunk-Based\nEnvironment branches: main=prod, staging, dev', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 78, title: 'Kustomize', description: 'แสดง "Tool: Kustomize", "Base: deployment.yaml, service.yaml", "Overlay dev: replicas=1, image=:dev", "Overlay staging: replicas=2, image=:staging", "Overlay prod: replicas=5, image=:v1.2.0", "Apply: kubectl apply -k overlays/prod/"', difficulty: 2, category: 'gitops', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Kustomize = Customize K8s manifests โดยไม่แก้ไฟล์ต้นฉบับ\n\nโครงสร้าง:\n  base/\n    deployment.yaml\n    service.yaml\n    kustomization.yaml\n  overlays/\n    dev/kustomization.yaml\n    staging/kustomization.yaml\n    prod/kustomization.yaml\n\nkustomization.yaml (overlay):\n  resources:\n    - ../../base\n  patches:\n    - patch-replicas.yaml\n  images:\n    - name: myapp\n      newTag: v1.2.0\n\nข้อดี:\n  - ไม่ต้อง template engine\n  - Base ไม่ถูกแก้ไข\n  - Built-in kubectl (kubectl apply -k)\n  - เหมาะกับ GitOps (ArgoCD รองรับ)', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Tool: Kustomize\nBase: deployment.yaml, service.yaml\nOverlay dev: replicas=1, image=:dev\nOverlay staging: replicas=2, image=:staging\nOverlay prod: replicas=5, image=:v1.2.0\nApply: kubectl apply -k overlays/prod/', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 79, title: 'Sealed Secrets', description: 'แสดง "Problem: K8s Secrets are base64 (not encrypted)", "Solution: Sealed Secrets", "Encrypt: kubeseal --cert cert.pem", "Store: SealedSecret in Git (safe!)", "Decrypt: only controller in cluster", "Rotate: re-encrypt with new cert"', difficulty: 2, category: 'gitops', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Sealed Secrets = เก็บ secrets ใน Git อย่างปลอดภัย\n\nปัญหา:\n  K8s Secret = base64 encoded (ไม่ปลอดภัย)\n  ไม่ควรเก็บใน Git!\n\nSolution: Bitnami Sealed Secrets\n  1. ติดตั้ง controller ใน cluster\n  2. Controller สร้าง key pair\n  3. Encrypt secret ด้วย public key (kubeseal)\n  4. เก็บ SealedSecret ใน Git\n  5. Controller decrypt ด้วย private key\n\nAlternatives:\n  External Secrets Operator = ดึงจาก Vault/AWS SM/Key Vault\n  SOPS = encrypt files ด้วย KMS\n  Vault = HashiCorp secrets management', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Problem: K8s Secrets are base64 (not encrypted)\nSolution: Sealed Secrets\nEncrypt: kubeseal --cert cert.pem\nStore: SealedSecret in Git (safe!)\nDecrypt: only controller in cluster\nRotate: re-encrypt with new cert', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 80, title: 'Flux CD', description: 'แสดง "Tool: Flux CD v2", "Source: GitRepository (github.com/org/config)", "Kustomization: apps/production", "HelmRelease: nginx-ingress", "ImagePolicy: auto-update tags", "Notification: Slack alerts"', difficulty: 2, category: 'gitops', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Flux CD = GitOps operator สำหรับ Kubernetes (CNCF)\n\nComponents:\n  Source Controller = watch Git repos, Helm repos\n  Kustomize Controller = apply Kustomize overlays\n  Helm Controller = manage Helm releases\n  Notification Controller = alerts (Slack, Teams)\n  Image Automation = auto-update image tags\n\nBootstrap:\n  flux bootstrap github \\\n    --owner=myorg \\\n    --repository=fleet-config \\\n    --path=clusters/production\n\nFlux vs ArgoCD:\n  Flux = CLI-first, lightweight, CNCF\n  ArgoCD = UI-first, feature-rich, CNCF\n  ทั้งคู่เป็น GitOps operator ที่ดี', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Tool: Flux CD v2\nSource: GitRepository (github.com/org/config)\nKustomization: apps/production\nHelmRelease: nginx-ingress\nImagePolicy: auto-update tags\nNotification: Slack alerts', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 81, title: 'GitOps Repository Structure', description: 'แสดง "app-repo: source code + Dockerfile", "config-repo: K8s manifests", "  clusters/production/", "  clusters/staging/", "  apps/frontend/", "  apps/backend/"', difficulty: 2, category: 'gitops', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 GitOps Repository Structure\n\nStrategy 1: Monorepo\n  config-repo/\n    apps/\n      frontend/ (base + overlays)\n      backend/\n    infrastructure/\n      monitoring/\n      ingress/\n    clusters/\n      production/\n      staging/\n\nStrategy 2: Repo per team\n  team-a-config/\n  team-b-config/\n  platform-config/\n\nBest Practices:\n  - แยก app repo กับ config repo\n  - CI อัพเดท image tag ใน config repo\n  - GitOps operator watch config repo\n  - ใช้ Kustomize overlays แยก environments', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'app-repo: source code + Dockerfile\nconfig-repo: K8s manifests\n  clusters/production/\n  clusters/staging/\n  apps/frontend/\n  apps/backend/', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 82, title: 'PR-Based GitOps Workflow', description: 'แสดง "1. CI builds image: myapp:abc123", "2. CI updates config repo (image tag)", "3. PR created automatically", "4. Review + approve PR", "5. Merge to main", "6. ArgoCD syncs to cluster"', difficulty: 2, category: 'gitops', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 PR-Based GitOps Workflow (แนะนำ)\n\nFlow:\n  1. Developer push code -> app repo\n  2. CI pipeline: build, test, push image\n  3. CI อัพเดท image tag ใน config repo (สร้าง PR)\n  4. Team review PR (ดู diff ของ manifests)\n  5. Approve + merge\n  6. GitOps operator detect change -> sync\n\nTools สำหรับ auto-update:\n  - Flux Image Automation\n  - Renovate Bot\n  - Custom CI script (sed/kustomize edit)\n\nข้อดี:\n  - ทุกการเปลี่ยนแปลงผ่าน PR\n  - Review ก่อน deploy\n  - Git history = deployment history\n  - Rollback = revert PR', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: '1. CI builds image: myapp:abc123\n2. CI updates config repo (image tag)\n3. PR created automatically\n4. Review + approve PR\n5. Merge to main\n6. ArgoCD syncs to cluster', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 83, title: 'Environment Promotion', description: 'แสดง "Promotion Strategy: Progressive", "dev: auto-deploy on merge", "staging: auto-deploy after dev success", "prod: manual approval required", "Rollback: git revert + auto-sync", "Validation: smoke tests per environment"', difficulty: 3, category: 'gitops', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Environment Promotion ใน GitOps\n\nStrategies:\n  1. Branch per environment\n     dev branch -> staging branch -> main (prod)\n     Promote = merge/cherry-pick\n\n  2. Directory per environment (แนะนำ)\n     overlays/dev, overlays/staging, overlays/prod\n     Promote = update image tag ใน overlay\n\n  3. Progressive Delivery\n     dev: auto-deploy\n     staging: auto after dev passes\n     prod: manual approval + canary\n\nValidation Gates:\n  - Automated tests per environment\n  - Smoke tests after deploy\n  - Canary analysis (error rate, latency)\n  - Manual approval for production', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Promotion Strategy: Progressive\ndev: auto-deploy on merge\nstaging: auto-deploy after dev success\nprod: manual approval required\nRollback: git revert + auto-sync\nValidation: smoke tests per environment', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 84, title: 'Drift Detection & Reconciliation', description: 'แสดง "Desired State: Git (3 replicas)", "Live State: Cluster (2 replicas)", "Drift: detected!", "Cause: manual kubectl scale", "Action: auto-reconcile to 3 replicas", "Prevention: RBAC + admission webhooks"', difficulty: 3, category: 'gitops', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Drift Detection = ตรวจจับเมื่อ cluster ไม่ตรงกับ Git\n\nสาเหตุ drift:\n  - kubectl edit/scale โดยตรง\n  - Helm upgrade จาก CLI\n  - Operator แก้ไข resources\n  - Resource ถูกลบ\n\nReconciliation:\n  GitOps operator เปรียบเทียบ desired (Git) vs live (cluster)\n  ถ้าไม่ตรง -> apply จาก Git ใหม่\n\nArgoCD:\n  Self-heal = auto-reconcile\n  Sync window = กำหนดเวลาที่ sync ได้\n\nPrevention:\n  - RBAC: จำกัดสิทธิ์ kubectl\n  - Admission webhooks: block manual changes\n  - Policy: OPA/Kyverno enforce GitOps', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Desired State: Git (3 replicas)\nLive State: Cluster (2 replicas)\nDrift: detected!\nCause: manual kubectl scale\nAction: auto-reconcile to 3 replicas\nPrevention: RBAC + admission webhooks', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 85, title: 'GitOps Security', description: 'แสดง "Secrets: External Secrets Operator", "RBAC: least privilege per namespace", "Policy: Kyverno (enforce labels, limits)", "Signing: cosign (verify images)", "Audit: Git log = who changed what", "Network: NetworkPolicy per service"', difficulty: 3, category: 'gitops', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 GitOps Security Best Practices\n\nSecrets Management:\n  - Sealed Secrets (encrypt in Git)\n  - External Secrets Operator (pull from Vault/AWS SM)\n  - SOPS (encrypt with KMS)\n\nImage Security:\n  - Sign images (cosign/Notary)\n  - Verify signatures before deploy\n  - Scan for vulnerabilities (Trivy)\n\nPolicy Enforcement:\n  Kyverno / OPA Gatekeeper:\n  - Require resource limits\n  - Require labels\n  - Block privileged containers\n  - Enforce image registry whitelist\n\nAccess Control:\n  - RBAC per namespace\n  - Git branch protection\n  - PR approval requirements\n  - Audit logging', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Secrets: External Secrets Operator\nRBAC: least privilege per namespace\nPolicy: Kyverno (enforce labels, limits)\nSigning: cosign (verify images)\nAudit: Git log = who changed what\nNetwork: NetworkPolicy per service', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 86, title: 'Progressive Delivery', description: 'แสดง "Strategy: Canary Deployment", "Step 1: 10% traffic to v2", "Step 2: Monitor error rate (< 1%)", "Step 3: 50% traffic to v2", "Step 4: 100% traffic to v2", "Tool: Argo Rollouts / Flagger"', difficulty: 3, category: 'gitops', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Progressive Delivery = deploy ทีละน้อย ตรวจสอบก่อนเพิ่ม\n\nStrategies:\n  Canary = ส่ง traffic ทีละ % (10 > 50 > 100)\n  Blue-Green = สลับระหว่าง 2 versions\n  A/B Testing = แบ่งตาม user segments\n\nArgo Rollouts:\n  apiVersion: argoproj.io/v1alpha1\n  kind: Rollout\n  spec:\n    strategy:\n      canary:\n        steps:\n        - setWeight: 10\n        - pause: { duration: 5m }\n        - setWeight: 50\n        - pause: { duration: 10m }\n\nAnalysis:\n  ตรวจสอบ metrics อัตโนมัติ (Prometheus)\n  ถ้า error rate สูง -> auto rollback', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Strategy: Canary Deployment\nStep 1: 10% traffic to v2\nStep 2: Monitor error rate (< 1%)\nStep 3: 50% traffic to v2\nStep 4: 100% traffic to v2\nTool: Argo Rollouts / Flagger', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 87, title: 'Multi-Cluster GitOps', description: 'แสดง "Hub Cluster: management", "Spoke: dev-cluster (us-east-1)", "Spoke: staging-cluster (eu-west-1)", "Spoke: prod-cluster (multi-region)", "Config: centralized Git repo", "Tool: ArgoCD ApplicationSet"', difficulty: 3, category: 'gitops', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Multi-Cluster GitOps = จัดการหลาย clusters จาก Git\n\nPatterns:\n  Hub-Spoke: 1 management cluster -> หลาย workload clusters\n  Standalone: ArgoCD ในแต่ละ cluster\n\nArgoCD ApplicationSet:\n  สร้าง Applications อัตโนมัติจาก template\n  Generators:\n    - List: กำหนด clusters เอง\n    - Cluster: ทุก registered clusters\n    - Git: ทุก directories ใน repo\n    - Matrix: combine generators\n\nFlux Multi-tenancy:\n  แยก config per cluster ใน Git\n  clusters/\n    dev/flux-system/\n    staging/flux-system/\n    prod/flux-system/', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Hub Cluster: management\nSpoke: dev-cluster (us-east-1)\nSpoke: staging-cluster (eu-west-1)\nSpoke: prod-cluster (multi-region)\nConfig: centralized Git repo\nTool: ArgoCD ApplicationSet', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 88, title: 'GitOps Disaster Recovery', description: 'แสดง "Scenario: Cluster destroyed", "Step 1: Provision new cluster (Terraform)", "Step 2: Install GitOps operator", "Step 3: Point to config Git repo", "Step 4: Auto-reconcile all apps", "Recovery Time: < 30 minutes"', difficulty: 3, category: 'gitops', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 GitOps Disaster Recovery\n\nข้อดีของ GitOps สำหรับ DR:\n  Git = single source of truth\n  ทุกอย่างอยู่ใน Git -> สร้างใหม่ได้ทั้งหมด\n\nDR Steps:\n  1. สร้าง cluster ใหม่ (Terraform)\n  2. ติดตั้ง ArgoCD/Flux\n  3. ชี้ไปที่ config repo เดิม\n  4. Operator reconcile ทุก apps อัตโนมัติ\n  5. DNS failover (Route53/Azure DNS)\n\nสิ่งที่ต้อง backup แยก:\n  - Persistent data (database snapshots)\n  - Secrets encryption keys\n  - Terraform state\n\nBest Practice: ซ้อม DR ทุก quarter', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Scenario: Cluster destroyed\nStep 1: Provision new cluster (Terraform)\nStep 2: Install GitOps operator\nStep 3: Point to config Git repo\nStep 4: Auto-reconcile all apps\nRecovery Time: < 30 minutes', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 89, title: 'GitOps Observability', description: 'แสดง "Deployment tracking: ArgoCD UI", "Sync status: 15 Synced, 1 OutOfSync", "Health: 14 Healthy, 2 Progressing", "Notifications: Slack #deployments", "Metrics: argocd_app_sync_total", "Dashboard: Grafana GitOps overview"', difficulty: 2, category: 'gitops', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 GitOps Observability = มองเห็นสถานะทั้งหมด\n\nArgoCD Dashboard:\n  - Application list + status\n  - Sync status (Synced/OutOfSync)\n  - Health status (Healthy/Degraded/Progressing)\n  - Resource tree visualization\n  - Diff view (desired vs live)\n\nNotifications:\n  Slack, Teams, Email, Webhook\n  Triggers: sync success/fail, health degraded\n\nMetrics (Prometheus):\n  argocd_app_info\n  argocd_app_sync_total\n  argocd_app_health_status\n\nGrafana Dashboards:\n  - Deployment frequency\n  - Sync duration\n  - Failed syncs\n  - Drift events', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Deployment tracking: ArgoCD UI\nSync status: 15 Synced, 1 OutOfSync\nHealth: 14 Healthy, 2 Progressing\nNotifications: Slack #deployments\nMetrics: argocd_app_sync_total\nDashboard: Grafana GitOps overview', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 90, title: 'GitOps Best Practices', description: 'แสดง "1. Separate app and config repos", "2. Use Kustomize or Helm for templating", "3. PR-based workflow for all changes", "4. Automate image tag updates", "5. Implement progressive delivery", "6. Monitor and alert on drift"', difficulty: 2, category: 'gitops', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 GitOps Best Practices Summary\n\n1. แยก app repo กับ config repo\n   - CI ไม่ต้อง access cluster\n   - Config repo = deployment history\n\n2. ใช้ Kustomize/Helm สำหรับ multi-env\n   - Base + overlays per environment\n\n3. ทุกการเปลี่ยนแปลงผ่าน PR\n   - Review, approve, merge\n   - Git history = audit trail\n\n4. Automate image updates\n   - CI อัพเดท tag ใน config repo\n\n5. Progressive delivery\n   - Canary/Blue-Green deployments\n   - Auto-rollback on failure\n\n6. Monitor drift\n   - Alert เมื่อ cluster ไม่ตรงกับ Git\n   - Self-heal อัตโนมัติ', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: '1. Separate app and config repos\n2. Use Kustomize or Helm for templating\n3. PR-based workflow for all changes\n4. Automate image tag updates\n5. Implement progressive delivery\n6. Monitor and alert on drift', validationType: 'exact' },

  // === ArgoCD (91-110) ===
  { id: 91, title: 'ArgoCD คืออะไร', description: 'แสดง "ArgoCD = GitOps Continuous Delivery for K8s", "Model: Pull-based (agent in cluster)", "UI: Web dashboard + CLI", "Sync: Git -> Kubernetes", "CNCF: Graduated project"', difficulty: 1, category: 'argocd', hint: 'echo 5 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 ArgoCD = GitOps CD tool สำหรับ Kubernetes (CNCF Graduated)\n\nทำงานอย่างไร:\n  1. ArgoCD รันใน K8s cluster\n  2. Watch Git repository\n  3. เปรียบเทียบ desired state (Git) vs live state (cluster)\n  4. Sync ให้ตรงกัน (manual หรือ auto)\n\nข้อดี:\n  - Web UI สวย ใช้งานง่าย\n  - CLI สำหรับ automation\n  - รองรับ Helm, Kustomize, plain YAML\n  - Multi-cluster management\n  - SSO integration (OIDC, SAML)\n  - Audit logging\n  - Webhook support', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'ArgoCD = GitOps Continuous Delivery for K8s\nModel: Pull-based (agent in cluster)\nUI: Web dashboard + CLI\nSync: Git -> Kubernetes\nCNCF: Graduated project', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 92, title: 'ArgoCD Installation', description: 'แสดง "Step 1: kubectl create namespace argocd", "Step 2: kubectl apply -n argocd -f install.yaml", "Step 3: kubectl port-forward svc/argocd-server 8080:443", "Step 4: argocd admin initial-password -n argocd", "Step 5: argocd login localhost:8080", "Status: ArgoCD ready!"', difficulty: 1, category: 'argocd', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 ArgoCD Installation\n\nBasic Install:\n  kubectl create namespace argocd\n  kubectl apply -n argocd -f \\\n    https://raw.githubusercontent.com/argoproj/argo-cd/stable/manifests/install.yaml\n\nHA Install (production):\n  kubectl apply -n argocd -f \\\n    https://raw.githubusercontent.com/argoproj/argo-cd/stable/manifests/ha/install.yaml\n\nAccess UI:\n  kubectl port-forward svc/argocd-server -n argocd 8080:443\n  เปิด https://localhost:8080\n\nInitial Password:\n  argocd admin initial-password -n argocd\n  เปลี่ยนรหัสผ่านทันที!\n\nHelm Install:\n  helm repo add argo https://argoproj.github.io/argo-helm\n  helm install argocd argo/argo-cd -n argocd', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Step 1: kubectl create namespace argocd\nStep 2: kubectl apply -n argocd -f install.yaml\nStep 3: kubectl port-forward svc/argocd-server 8080:443\nStep 4: argocd admin initial-password -n argocd\nStep 5: argocd login localhost:8080\nStatus: ArgoCD ready!', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 93, title: 'ArgoCD Application', description: 'แสดง "Application: web-frontend", "Project: default", "Source: https://github.com/org/config.git", "Path: apps/frontend/overlays/prod", "Destination: https://kubernetes.default.svc", "Namespace: production"', difficulty: 2, category: 'argocd', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 ArgoCD Application = หน่วยหลักของ ArgoCD\n\nApplication YAML:\n  apiVersion: argoproj.io/v1alpha1\n  kind: Application\n  metadata:\n    name: web-frontend\n    namespace: argocd\n  spec:\n    project: default\n    source:\n      repoURL: https://github.com/org/config.git\n      path: apps/frontend/overlays/prod\n      targetRevision: main\n    destination:\n      server: https://kubernetes.default.svc\n      namespace: production\n    syncPolicy:\n      automated:\n        selfHeal: true\n        prune: true\n\nSource Types: Directory (YAML), Kustomize, Helm, Jsonnet', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Application: web-frontend\nProject: default\nSource: https://github.com/org/config.git\nPath: apps/frontend/overlays/prod\nDestination: https://kubernetes.default.svc\nNamespace: production', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 94, title: 'ArgoCD Sync Policies', description: 'แสดง "Manual Sync: click sync button", "Auto Sync: sync on Git change", "Self Heal: revert manual changes", "Prune: delete removed resources", "Sync Window: Mon-Fri 9AM-5PM", "Retry: 5 attempts, 10s backoff"', difficulty: 2, category: 'argocd', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 ArgoCD Sync Policies\n\nManual Sync:\n  argocd app sync web-frontend\n  หรือกดปุ่ม Sync ใน UI\n\nAutomated Sync:\n  syncPolicy:\n    automated:\n      prune: true      # ลบ resources ที่ไม่อยู่ใน Git\n      selfHeal: true   # แก้ไข manual changes\n      allowEmpty: false # ป้องกัน sync empty\n\nSync Options:\n  - CreateNamespace=true\n  - PruneLast=true\n  - ApplyOutOfSyncOnly=true\n\nSync Windows:\n  จำกัดเวลาที่ sync ได้ (เช่น ไม่ sync ตอนกลางคืน)\n\nRetry:\n  syncPolicy:\n    retry:\n      limit: 5\n      backoff: { duration: 10s, factor: 2 }', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Manual Sync: click sync button\nAuto Sync: sync on Git change\nSelf Heal: revert manual changes\nPrune: delete removed resources\nSync Window: Mon-Fri 9AM-5PM\nRetry: 5 attempts, 10s backoff', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 95, title: 'ArgoCD Projects', description: 'แสดง "Project: team-frontend", "Source Repos: github.com/org/frontend-*", "Destinations: prod-cluster/frontend-ns", "Cluster Resources: deny all", "Namespace Resources: allow deployments,services", "Roles: frontend-team (sync, get)"', difficulty: 2, category: 'argocd', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 ArgoCD Projects = จำกัดขอบเขตของ Applications\n\nAppProject:\n  apiVersion: argoproj.io/v1alpha1\n  kind: AppProject\n  spec:\n    sourceRepos:\n      - \"https://github.com/org/frontend-*\"\n    destinations:\n      - namespace: frontend-ns\n        server: https://prod-cluster\n    clusterResourceWhitelist: []\n    namespaceResourceWhitelist:\n      - group: apps\n        kind: Deployment\n      - group: \"\"\n        kind: Service\n\nใช้สำหรับ:\n  - Multi-tenancy (แยก team)\n  - จำกัด repos ที่ใช้ได้\n  - จำกัด clusters/namespaces\n  - จำกัด resource types', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Project: team-frontend\nSource Repos: github.com/org/frontend-*\nDestinations: prod-cluster/frontend-ns\nCluster Resources: deny all\nNamespace Resources: allow deployments,services\nRoles: frontend-team (sync, get)', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 96, title: 'ArgoCD with Helm', description: 'แสดง "Source Type: Helm", "Chart: oci://registry/charts/webapp", "Version: 1.5.0", "Values: values-prod.yaml", "Parameters: replicas=3, image.tag=v2.1", "Release: web-frontend"', difficulty: 2, category: 'argocd', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 ArgoCD + Helm\n\nHelm Chart จาก Git:\n  source:\n    repoURL: https://github.com/org/config\n    path: charts/webapp\n    helm:\n      valueFiles:\n        - values-prod.yaml\n      parameters:\n        - name: replicas\n          value: \"3\"\n\nHelm Chart จาก Registry:\n  source:\n    repoURL: https://charts.example.com\n    chart: webapp\n    targetRevision: 1.5.0\n    helm:\n      values: |\n        replicas: 3\n        image:\n          tag: v2.1\n\nOCI Registry:\n  source:\n    repoURL: oci://registry/charts\n    chart: webapp', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Source Type: Helm\nChart: oci://registry/charts/webapp\nVersion: 1.5.0\nValues: values-prod.yaml\nParameters: replicas=3, image.tag=v2.1\nRelease: web-frontend', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 97, title: 'App of Apps Pattern', description: 'แสดง "Root App: platform-apps", "  Child: frontend (Synced, Healthy)", "  Child: backend (Synced, Healthy)", "  Child: database (Synced, Healthy)", "  Child: monitoring (Synced, Progressing)", "  Child: ingress (Synced, Healthy)"', difficulty: 3, category: 'argocd', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 App of Apps = จัดการหลาย Applications ด้วย 1 root app\n\nRoot Application ชี้ไปที่ directory ที่มี Application manifests:\n  apps/\n    frontend.yaml    # ArgoCD Application\n    backend.yaml     # ArgoCD Application\n    database.yaml    # ArgoCD Application\n    monitoring.yaml  # ArgoCD Application\n\nRoot App:\n  source:\n    path: apps/\n  syncPolicy:\n    automated: {}\n\nข้อดี:\n  - Bootstrap ทั้ง cluster ด้วย 1 app\n  - เพิ่ม/ลบ apps ผ่าน Git\n  - Hierarchical management\n\nAlternative: ApplicationSet (ยืดหยุ่นกว่า)', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Root App: platform-apps\n  Child: frontend (Synced, Healthy)\n  Child: backend (Synced, Healthy)\n  Child: database (Synced, Healthy)\n  Child: monitoring (Synced, Progressing)\n  Child: ingress (Synced, Healthy)', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 98, title: 'ArgoCD ApplicationSet', description: 'แสดง "ApplicationSet: multi-env-apps", "Generator: Git directories", "Template: Application per directory", "Generated: dev-frontend, staging-frontend, prod-frontend", "Generated: dev-backend, staging-backend, prod-backend", "Total: 6 applications auto-created"', difficulty: 3, category: 'argocd', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 ApplicationSet = สร้าง Applications อัตโนมัติจาก template\n\nGenerators:\n  List = กำหนดค่าเอง\n  Cluster = ทุก registered clusters\n  Git Directory = ทุก directories ใน repo\n  Git File = อ่านค่าจากไฟล์\n  Matrix = combine 2 generators\n  Merge = merge หลาย generators\n\nตัวอย่าง Git Directory:\n  apiVersion: argoproj.io/v1alpha1\n  kind: ApplicationSet\n  spec:\n    generators:\n    - git:\n        repoURL: https://github.com/org/config\n        directories:\n        - path: apps/*/overlays/*\n    template:\n      metadata:\n        name: \"{{path.basename}}-{{path[2]}}\"\n      spec:\n        source:\n          path: \"{{path}}\"', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'ApplicationSet: multi-env-apps\nGenerator: Git directories\nTemplate: Application per directory\nGenerated: dev-frontend, staging-frontend, prod-frontend\nGenerated: dev-backend, staging-backend, prod-backend\nTotal: 6 applications auto-created', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 99, title: 'ArgoCD Multi-Cluster', description: 'แสดง "Management: argocd-cluster", "Registered Clusters:", "  dev: https://dev-api:6443 (connected)", "  staging: https://staging-api:6443 (connected)", "  prod-us: https://prod-us-api:6443 (connected)", "  prod-eu: https://prod-eu-api:6443 (connected)"', difficulty: 3, category: 'argocd', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 ArgoCD Multi-Cluster Management\n\nเพิ่ม Cluster:\n  argocd cluster add staging-context\n  argocd cluster list\n\nApplication ระบุ destination:\n  destination:\n    server: https://staging-api:6443\n    namespace: default\n\nPatterns:\n  1. Hub-Spoke: 1 ArgoCD -> หลาย clusters\n  2. Per-cluster: ArgoCD ในแต่ละ cluster\n\nApplicationSet + Cluster Generator:\n  generators:\n  - clusters:\n      selector:\n        matchLabels:\n          env: production\n  สร้าง app ในทุก production clusters\n\nSecurity:\n  - ArgoCD ใช้ ServiceAccount per cluster\n  - จำกัดสิทธิ์ด้วย RBAC\n  - Network: VPN/PrivateLink ระหว่าง clusters', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Management: argocd-cluster\nRegistered Clusters:\n  dev: https://dev-api:6443 (connected)\n  staging: https://staging-api:6443 (connected)\n  prod-us: https://prod-us-api:6443 (connected)\n  prod-eu: https://prod-eu-api:6443 (connected)', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 100, title: 'ArgoCD RBAC & SSO', description: 'แสดง "SSO: GitHub OAuth", "Role: admin (full access)", "Role: developer (apps: get,sync)", "Role: viewer (apps: get only)", "Policy: p, role:developer, applications, sync, */*, allow", "Default: role:readonly"', difficulty: 3, category: 'argocd', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 ArgoCD RBAC & SSO\n\nSSO Integration:\n  OIDC: GitHub, Google, Okta, Azure AD\n  SAML: OneLogin, ADFS\n  Dex: built-in identity broker\n\nRBAC Policy (argocd-rbac-cm):\n  policy.csv: |\n    p, role:developer, applications, get, */*, allow\n    p, role:developer, applications, sync, */*, allow\n    p, role:viewer, applications, get, */*, allow\n    g, github-org:dev-team, role:developer\n    g, github-org:ops-team, role:admin\n  policy.default: role:readonly\n\nScoped Access:\n  p, role:team-a, applications, *, team-a/*, allow\n  จำกัดให้เห็นเฉพาะ apps ใน project team-a', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'SSO: GitHub OAuth\nRole: admin (full access)\nRole: developer (apps: get,sync)\nRole: viewer (apps: get only)\nPolicy: p, role:developer, applications, sync, */*, allow\nDefault: role:readonly', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 101, title: 'ArgoCD Notifications', description: 'แสดง "Service: Slack (#deployments)", "Service: Teams (DevOps channel)", "Trigger: on-sync-succeeded", "Trigger: on-sync-failed", "Trigger: on-health-degraded", "Template: App {{.app.metadata.name}} is {{.app.status.sync.status}}"', difficulty: 2, category: 'argocd', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 ArgoCD Notifications\n\nServices:\n  Slack, Microsoft Teams, Email, Webhook, Grafana, PagerDuty\n\nConfiguration (argocd-notifications-cm):\n  service.slack: |\n    token: $slack-token\n  trigger.on-sync-succeeded: |\n    - when: app.status.sync.status == \"Synced\"\n      send: [app-sync-succeeded]\n  template.app-sync-succeeded: |\n    message: |\n      App {{.app.metadata.name}} synced!\n\nAnnotate Application:\n  metadata:\n    annotations:\n      notifications.argoproj.io/subscribe.on-sync-succeeded.slack: deployments\n\nTriggers:\n  on-sync-succeeded, on-sync-failed\n  on-health-degraded, on-deployed\n  on-sync-status-unknown', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Service: Slack (#deployments)\nService: Teams (DevOps channel)\nTrigger: on-sync-succeeded\nTrigger: on-sync-failed\nTrigger: on-health-degraded\nTemplate: App {{.app.metadata.name}} is {{.app.status.sync.status}}', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 102, title: 'ArgoCD Image Updater', description: 'แสดง "Tool: ArgoCD Image Updater", "Registry: ECR (220233744739.dkr.ecr.us-east-1.amazonaws.com)", "App: web-frontend", "Strategy: semver (latest stable)", "Current: v1.4.2", "Updated: v1.5.0 (auto-committed to Git)"', difficulty: 3, category: 'argocd', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 ArgoCD Image Updater = อัพเดท container images อัตโนมัติ\n\nทำงาน:\n  1. Watch container registries\n  2. ตรวจจับ image tag ใหม่\n  3. อัพเดท Application (หรือ commit กลับ Git)\n\nUpdate Strategies:\n  semver = latest semantic version (v1.5.0 > v1.4.2)\n  latest = latest tag\n  digest = latest digest\n  name = alphabetical\n\nAnnotations:\n  argocd-image-updater.argoproj.io/image-list: web=myrepo/web\n  argocd-image-updater.argoproj.io/web.update-strategy: semver\n\nWrite-back Methods:\n  argocd = อัพเดท Application โดยตรง\n  git = commit กลับ Git repo (แนะนำ)', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Tool: ArgoCD Image Updater\nRegistry: ECR (220233744739.dkr.ecr.us-east-1.amazonaws.com)\nApp: web-frontend\nStrategy: semver (latest stable)\nCurrent: v1.4.2\nUpdated: v1.5.0 (auto-committed to Git)', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 103, title: 'ArgoCD Rollback', description: 'แสดง "App: web-frontend", "History:", "  Rev 5: v1.5.0 (current - degraded)", "  Rev 4: v1.4.2 (healthy)", "  Rev 3: v1.4.1 (healthy)", "Action: rollback to Rev 4 (v1.4.2)"', difficulty: 2, category: 'argocd', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 ArgoCD Rollback\n\nดู History:\n  argocd app history web-frontend\n\nRollback:\n  argocd app rollback web-frontend 4\n\nUI: Application > History > Rollback\n\nGitOps Way (แนะนำ):\n  git revert <commit-hash>\n  ArgoCD จะ auto-sync กลับไป version เดิม\n\nข้อดี git revert:\n  - มี audit trail ใน Git\n  - ทุกคนเห็นว่า rollback\n  - Reproducible\n\nข้อเสีย argocd rollback:\n  - ไม่อัพเดท Git\n  - ถ้า auto-sync เปิด จะ sync กลับไป version ใหม่\n  - ต้องปิด auto-sync ก่อน rollback', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'App: web-frontend\nHistory:\n  Rev 5: v1.5.0 (current - degraded)\n  Rev 4: v1.4.2 (healthy)\n  Rev 3: v1.4.1 (healthy)\nAction: rollback to Rev 4 (v1.4.2)', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 104, title: 'ArgoCD + Argo Rollouts', description: 'แสดง "Rollout: web-frontend", "Strategy: Canary", "Step 1: setWeight 10% (pause 5m)", "Step 2: setWeight 50% (analysis)", "Step 3: setWeight 100%", "Analysis: prometheus (error-rate < 1%)"', difficulty: 3, category: 'argocd', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Argo Rollouts = Progressive Delivery สำหรับ K8s\n\nCanary:\n  spec:\n    strategy:\n      canary:\n        steps:\n        - setWeight: 10\n        - pause: { duration: 5m }\n        - setWeight: 50\n        - analysis:\n            templates:\n            - templateName: success-rate\n        - setWeight: 100\n\nAnalysisTemplate:\n  metrics:\n  - name: success-rate\n    provider:\n      prometheus:\n        query: |\n          sum(rate(http_requests_total{status=~\"2..\"}[5m]))\n          / sum(rate(http_requests_total[5m]))\n    successCondition: result[0] > 0.99\n\nBlue-Green:\n  strategy:\n    blueGreen:\n      activeService: web-active\n      previewService: web-preview\n      autoPromotionEnabled: false', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Rollout: web-frontend\nStrategy: Canary\nStep 1: setWeight 10% (pause 5m)\nStep 2: setWeight 50% (analysis)\nStep 3: setWeight 100%\nAnalysis: prometheus (error-rate < 1%)', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 105, title: 'ArgoCD Disaster Recovery', description: 'แสดง "Backup: argocd-util export > backup.yaml", "Components: Applications, Projects, Repos, RBAC", "Restore: argocd-util import < backup.yaml", "HA Mode: 3 replicas (API, Repo, Controller)", "Redis: HA with Sentinel", "Recovery: < 15 minutes"', difficulty: 3, category: 'argocd', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 ArgoCD Disaster Recovery\n\nBackup:\n  argocd admin export > backup.yaml\n  เก็บ: Applications, Projects, Repos, Clusters, RBAC\n\nRestore:\n  argocd admin import < backup.yaml\n\nHA Installation:\n  - API Server: 3+ replicas\n  - Repo Server: 3+ replicas\n  - Application Controller: 1 (leader election)\n  - Redis: HA with Sentinel\n\nBest Practices:\n  - Applications อยู่ใน Git (App of Apps)\n  - ไม่ต้อง backup apps ถ้าใช้ GitOps ถูกต้อง\n  - Backup เฉพาะ Projects, RBAC, Repos config\n  - ใช้ Helm/Kustomize install ArgoCD (reproducible)', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Backup: argocd-util export > backup.yaml\nComponents: Applications, Projects, Repos, RBAC\nRestore: argocd-util import < backup.yaml\nHA Mode: 3 replicas (API, Repo, Controller)\nRedis: HA with Sentinel\nRecovery: < 15 minutes', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 106, title: 'ArgoCD Monitoring', description: 'แสดง "Metrics: /metrics (Prometheus)", "argocd_app_info: 15 apps", "argocd_app_sync_total: 142 syncs", "argocd_app_reconcile: avg 2.3s", "Grafana Dashboard: ArgoCD Overview", "Alert: sync failed > 0 for 5m"', difficulty: 2, category: 'argocd', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 ArgoCD Monitoring\n\nPrometheus Metrics:\n  argocd_app_info = app metadata\n  argocd_app_sync_total = sync count\n  argocd_app_reconcile_duration = reconcile time\n  argocd_app_health_status = health per app\n  argocd_cluster_info = cluster status\n\nGrafana Dashboards:\n  - ArgoCD Overview (apps, syncs, health)\n  - ArgoCD Performance (reconcile time, queue depth)\n  - ArgoCD Notifications (sent, failed)\n\nAlerts:\n  - App sync failed\n  - App health degraded\n  - High reconcile duration\n  - Cluster connection lost\n\nServiceMonitor:\n  apiVersion: monitoring.coreos.com/v1\n  kind: ServiceMonitor\n  spec:\n    selector:\n      matchLabels:\n        app.kubernetes.io/name: argocd-server', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Metrics: /metrics (Prometheus)\nargocd_app_info: 15 apps\nargocd_app_sync_total: 142 syncs\nargocd_app_reconcile: avg 2.3s\nGrafana Dashboard: ArgoCD Overview\nAlert: sync failed > 0 for 5m', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 107, title: 'ArgoCD Best Practices', description: 'แสดง "1. Use App of Apps or ApplicationSet", "2. Enable auto-sync + self-heal + prune", "3. Use Projects for multi-tenancy", "4. Integrate SSO (GitHub/Azure AD)", "5. Monitor with Prometheus + Grafana", "6. Backup RBAC and Project configs"', difficulty: 2, category: 'argocd', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 ArgoCD Best Practices\n\n1. App of Apps / ApplicationSet\n   - Bootstrap ทั้ง cluster จาก Git\n   - เพิ่ม/ลบ apps ผ่าน PR\n\n2. Auto-sync + Self-heal + Prune\n   - ให้ ArgoCD จัดการทุกอย่าง\n   - ป้องกัน drift\n\n3. Projects สำหรับ multi-tenancy\n   - จำกัด repos, clusters, resources per team\n\n4. SSO Integration\n   - ไม่ใช้ local accounts\n   - RBAC ตาม GitHub teams/Azure AD groups\n\n5. Monitoring\n   - Prometheus metrics\n   - Grafana dashboards\n   - Slack notifications\n\n6. Declarative Setup\n   - ArgoCD config ใน Git (GitOps for GitOps)\n   - Reproducible installation', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: '1. Use App of Apps or ApplicationSet\n2. Enable auto-sync + self-heal + prune\n3. Use Projects for multi-tenancy\n4. Integrate SSO (GitHub/Azure AD)\n5. Monitor with Prometheus + Grafana\n6. Backup RBAC and Project configs', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 108, title: 'ArgoCD Troubleshooting', description: 'แสดง "Issue: App stuck OutOfSync", "Check 1: argocd app diff web-frontend", "Check 2: argocd app get web-frontend", "Check 3: kubectl logs -n argocd argocd-application-controller", "Check 4: Verify Git repo access", "Fix: argocd app sync --force web-frontend"', difficulty: 3, category: 'argocd', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 ArgoCD Troubleshooting\n\nCommon Issues:\n\n1. OutOfSync แต่ sync ไม่ได้:\n   argocd app diff my-app  # ดู diff\n   อาจเป็น: resource ถูกแก้ไขโดย operator\n   Fix: ignoreDifferences ใน Application\n\n2. ComparisonError:\n   CRD ยังไม่ถูกติดตั้ง\n   Fix: ติดตั้ง CRDs ก่อน หรือใช้ sync waves\n\n3. Sync failed:\n   kubectl logs -n argocd argocd-application-controller\n   อาจเป็น: RBAC, resource quota, invalid manifest\n\n4. Slow sync:\n   เพิ่ม repo-server replicas\n   ใช้ shallow clone\n\n5. Git access denied:\n   ตรวจสอบ SSH key / token\n   argocd repo list', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Issue: App stuck OutOfSync\nCheck 1: argocd app diff web-frontend\nCheck 2: argocd app get web-frontend\nCheck 3: kubectl logs -n argocd argocd-application-controller\nCheck 4: Verify Git repo access\nFix: argocd app sync --force web-frontend', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 109, title: 'ArgoCD + Crossplane', description: 'แสดง "Crossplane: K8s-native cloud provisioning", "Provider: AWS, Azure, GCP", "XRD: CompositeDatabase", "Claim: PostgreSQL (size: small)", "ArgoCD: manages Crossplane resources via Git", "Result: Cloud resources as K8s objects"', difficulty: 3, category: 'argocd', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 ArgoCD + Crossplane = GitOps for Cloud Infrastructure\n\nCrossplane:\n  - Provision cloud resources ผ่าน K8s API\n  - เขียน YAML เหมือน K8s resources\n  - ArgoCD จัดการ Crossplane resources ผ่าน Git\n\nComposite Resources:\n  XRD = define custom API\n  Composition = map to cloud resources\n  Claim = request resources\n\nตัวอย่าง:\n  apiVersion: database.example.com/v1\n  kind: PostgreSQL\n  spec:\n    size: small\n    region: us-east-1\n\nCrossplane สร้าง RDS instance ให้อัตโนมัติ!\n\nGitOps Flow:\n  Git -> ArgoCD -> Crossplane -> AWS/Azure/GCP', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Crossplane: K8s-native cloud provisioning\nProvider: AWS, Azure, GCP\nXRD: CompositeDatabase\nClaim: PostgreSQL (size: small)\nArgoCD: manages Crossplane resources via Git\nResult: Cloud resources as K8s objects', validationType: 'exact' },
  { id: 110, title: 'Full GitOps Architecture', description: 'แสดง "Source: GitHub (app + config repos)", "CI: GitHub Actions (build, test, scan, push)", "CD: ArgoCD (sync from config repo)", "Infra: Terraform + Atlantis", "Secrets: External Secrets + Key Vault", "Observe: Prometheus + Grafana + Loki + Tempo"', difficulty: 3, category: 'argocd', hint: 'echo 6 บรรทัด', lesson: '📖 Complete GitOps Architecture\n\nSource:\n  App Repo = source code + Dockerfile + CI\n  Config Repo = K8s manifests (Kustomize/Helm)\n\nCI (GitHub Actions):\n  Build -> Test -> Scan (Trivy) -> Push image\n  -> Update image tag in config repo\n\nCD (ArgoCD):\n  Watch config repo -> Sync to K8s\n  Auto-sync + Self-heal + Prune\n  Progressive delivery (Argo Rollouts)\n\nInfrastructure:\n  Terraform + Atlantis (PR-based)\n  Crossplane (K8s-native)\n\nSecurity:\n  External Secrets Operator\n  Kyverno policies\n  Image signing (cosign)\n\nObservability:\n  Prometheus + Grafana (metrics)\n  Loki (logs), Tempo (traces)\n  ArgoCD notifications (Slack)', initialCode: '#!/bin/bash\n', expectedOutput: 'Source: GitHub (app + config repos)\nCI: GitHub Actions (build, test, scan, push)\nCD: ArgoCD (sync from config repo)\nInfra: Terraform + Atlantis\nSecrets: External Secrets + Key Vault\nObserve: Prometheus + Grafana + Loki + Tempo', validationType: 'exact' },
];
